{"type":"message","id":"633c923b","parentId":"5047d6a9","timestamp":"2026-03-30T03:41:48.455Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I see clearly:\n- Aggressive journal file has only 1 line (header only, no data rows) → 0 journal records\n- Defensive journal has 2 lines (1 header + 1 data row) → 1 journal record\n- Balanced journal has 2 lines (1 header + 1 data row) → 1 journal record\n\nSo the issue is that aggressive had 0 journal records (empty file except header) despite having 12 planned orders, while the other two had 1 journal record each.\n\nLet me also check the proposed orders to understand what happened.","thinkingSignature":"919a483439accc37511cd2a646084e68ce21f4b16b39b3b044101988d439e0f5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_m2zvbsv7w3kv_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_aggressive_trading_journal_20260327.csv"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_m2zvbsv7w3kv_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_aggressive_merged_proposed_orders_20260327.csv | head -5"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":12501,"output":243,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":37764,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774842102261,"responseId":"061923f64ef2dc32e5d53f23225c0d4f"}}
