{"type":"message","id":"8f6d4919","parentId":"2c15ca0b","timestamp":"2026-03-30T03:41:48.640Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_m2zvbsv7w3kv_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"trade_date,ts_code,action,target_value,target_weight,target_qty,ref_price,strategy_id,score,risk_adjustment,risk_status,exit_type,exit_reason,reduce_score,reduce_rank_reason,reason,source_signal_file,generated_at,approved,ai_stock_name,ai_operation_advice,ai_trend_prediction,ai_sentiment_score,ai_decision,ai_budget_scale,ai_score_scale,ai_gate_reason,ai_analysis_status,ai_analysis_time,ai_analysis_summary,ai_risk_warning,ai_stop_loss,ai_take_profit,ai_no_position_advice,ai_has_position_advice,ai_rsi14,ai_rsi_signal,ai_realtime_source,ai_realtime_price,ai_realtime_change_pct,ai_realtime_confirmed\n2026-03-27,002074.SZ,BUY,83706.83361344539,0.0840336134453781,,,smallcap_chip_v4_2,0.566961,none|scale_total_exposure,normal,,,,,auto_live_v4_2,/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/signals/merged/merged_signals_20260327.csv,2026-03-30T09:18:15.185658+08:00,True,国轩高科,观望,震荡,45,reduce,0.25,0.25,股票分析建议=观望 | 评分=45,cache,2026-03-30T09:04:13.731057,国轩高科当前处于震荡盘整阶段，均线系统（MA5、MA10、MA20）高度粘合，未形成明确的多头或空头排列，趋势方向不明。价格虽在MA5附近且乖离率安全，但核心的多头排列条件不满足。筹码结构显示套牢盘较重，上行阻力较大。综合技术面与筹码面，不符合趋势交易‘顺势而为’的核心原则，建议耐心等待方向选择。,主要风险在于技术趋势未明，若无法放量突破均线压制，可能延续震荡或转弱。筹码结构不佳，反弹面临大量解套抛压。,36.3,38.53,空仓者建议：当前趋势不明，不符合多头排列原则，应保持观望，等待股价站上MA20且均线形成多头排列后再考虑。,持仓者建议：若成本不高可继续持有，但需密切关注MA20支撑（37.46元），若放量跌破应考虑减仓。,,,tencent,37.6,0.0,True\n2026-03-27,002240.SZ,BUY,75336.15025210084,0.0756302521008403,,,smallcap_chip_v4_2|smallcap_chip_v4_2b,0.7164065,none|scale_total_exposure,normal,,,,,auto_live_v4_2 | auto_live_v4_2b_fundamental_guard,/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/signals/merged/merged_signals_20260327.csv,2026-03-30T09:18:15.185658+08:00,True,盛新锂能,观望,震荡,47,reduce,0.25,0.25,股票分析建议=观望 | 评分=47,cache,2026-03-30T09:03:18.861672