{"type":"message","id":"04b563ef","parentId":"8f6d4919","timestamp":"2026-03-30T03:42:00.195Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand the full picture. Let me summarize:\n\n1. **Aggressive 的 journal 是空的**（只有 header，0 条数据），但有 12 条计划订单（proposed orders）\n2. **Defensive 和 Balanced 各自有 1 条 journal 记录**\n\n这意味着在 20260327，aggressive 策略：\n- 生成了 12 个买入/卖出订单\n- 但这些订单**没有任何一条被写入 journal**（可能是执行失败、或写入失败）\n- 守卫规则检测到\"有计划订单但没有执行记录\"，触发 `NO_JOURNAL_WITH_PLANNED_ORDERS` RED 告警\n\n\n- 这不是风控参数本身更严格，而是 aggressive 的执行链路在这一天出现了问题，导致没有任何订单被记录\n\n问题可能出在 proposed orders 阶段就被拦下了，或者执行后写 journal 失败了。aggressive 的高杠杆持仓风格（12 个仓位）在高波动环境下更容易触发风控拦截，阻止订单进入执行阶段。\n\n更深层的原因可能是激进策略在市场下跌时持仓更重或使用了更大的风险敞口，导致链条中某个环节出现了问题。","thinkingSignature":"543f731cd5eb5374d93fdb1221987d6171e8e1c634135f4add6ddfd69398d0d5"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_j0z3ykr0h5g8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_aggressive_merged_proposed_orders_20260327.csv | wc -l"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_j0z3ykr0h5g8_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -c \"BUY\\|SELL\" /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_aggressive_merged_proposed_orders_20260327.csv"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":14576,"output":364,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":39960,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774842108640,"responseId":"061923fca9080f8c478083c7c142273a"}}
