{"type":"message","id":"3e8036ed","parentId":"8bf60023","timestamp":"2026-03-30T03:51:51.230Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2rjzua0khmwd_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def resolve_pretrade_state(paper_cfg: dict[str, Any], date_tag: str) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    profile_slug = profile_slug_from_config(paper_cfg)\n    initial_cash = parse_float(paper_cfg.get(\"initial_cash\"), 0.0)\n    start_date_tag = parse_optional_date_tag(paper_cfg.get(\"start_date_tag\", \"\"))\n    if initial_cash <= 0:\n        raise ValueError(\"paper trading config 的 initial_cash 必须大于 0\")\n\n    if start_date_tag and date_tag <= start_date_tag:\n        return {\n            \"available_cash\": initial_cash,\n            \"account_nav\": initial_cash,\n            \"positions_df\": pd.DataFrame(columns=[\"symbol\", \"quantity\", \"cost_price\"]),\n            \"source\": \"initial_capital\",\n            \"source_date_tag\": \"\",\n        }\n\n    prior_account_path = find_latest_prior_account(REPORT_DIR, date_tag, profile_slug=profile_slug)\n    if prior_account_path is None:\n        return {\n            \"available_cash\": initial_cash,\n            \"account_nav\": initial_cash,\n            \"positions_df\": pd.DataFrame(columns=[\"symbol\", \"quantity\", \"cost_price\"]),\n            \"source\": \"initial_capital_fallback\",\n            \"source_date_tag\": \"\",\n        }\n\n    payload = load_json(prior_account_path)\n    source_date_tag = extract_date_tag(prior_account_path)\n    files = payload.get(\"files\", {}) or {}\n    positions_path = None\n    if files.get(\"positions_dated\"):\n        candidate = Path(str(files.get(\"positions_dated\")))\n        positions_path = candidate if candidate.exists() else None\n    if positions_path is None:\n        fallback = report_path(REPORT_DIR, \"positions_dated\", profile_slug=profile_slug, date_tag=source_date_tag)\n        positions_path = fallback if fallback.exists() else None\n\n    positions_df = load_positions_snapshot(positions_path)\n    available_cash = parse_float(payload.get(\"cash\"), initial_cash)\n    account_nav = parse_float(payload.get(\"nav\"), available_cash)\n    if available_cash <= 0:\n        available_cash = max(account_nav, initial_cash)\n    if account_nav <= 0:\n        account_nav = max(available_cash, initial_cash)\n\n    return {\n        \"available_cash\": available_cash,\n        \"account_nav\": account_nav,\n        \"positions_df\": positions_df,\n        \"source\": \"prior_account_snapshot\",\n        \"source_date_tag\": source_date_tag,\n        \"source_file\": str(prior_account_path),\n    }\n\n\ndef resolve_tickets_path(date_tag: str, tickets_arg: str) -> Path:\n    if tickets_arg:\n        path = resolve_path(tickets_arg)\n        if not path.exists():\n            raise FileNotFoundError(f\"未找到指定票据文件: {path}\")\n        return path\n    preferred = REPORT_DIR / f\"paper_signal_tickets_{date_tag}.csv\"\n    if preferred.exists():\n        return preferred\n    dated = REPORT_DIR / f\"stock_signal_tickets_live_{date_tag}.csv\"\n    if dated.exists():\n        return dated\n    legacy = REPORT_DIR / f\"stock_signal_tickets_{date_tag}.csv\"\n    if legacy.exists():\n        return legacy\n    raise FileNotFoundError(f\"缺少指定日期的票据文件: {dated}\")"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":32,"aggregated":"def resolve_pretrade_state(paper_cfg: dict[str, Any], date_tag: str) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    profile_slug = profile_slug_from_config(paper_cfg)\n    initial_cash = parse_float(paper_cfg.get(\"initial_cash\"), 0.0)\n    start_date_tag = parse_optional_date_tag(paper_cfg.get(\"start_date_tag\", \"\"))\n    if initial_cash <= 0:\n        raise ValueError(\"paper trading config 的 initial_cash 必须大于 0\")\n\n    if start_date_tag and date_tag <= start_date_tag:\n        return {\n            \"available_cash\": initial_cash,\n            \"account_nav\": initial_cash,\n            \"positions_df\": pd.DataFrame(columns=[\"symbol\", \"quantity\", \"cost_price\"]),\n            \"source\": \"initial_capital\",\n            \"source_date_tag\": \"\",\n        }\n\n    prior_account_path = find_latest_prior_account(REPORT_DIR, date_tag, profile_slug=profile_slug)\n    if prior_account_path is None:\n        return {\n            \"available_cash\": initial_cash,\n            \"account_nav\": initial_cash,\n            \"positions_df\": pd.DataFrame(columns=[\"symbol\", \"quantity\", \"cost_price\"]),\n            \"source\": \"initial_capital_fallback\",\n            \"source_date_tag\": \"\",\n        }\n\n    payload = load_json(prior_account_path)\n    source_date_tag = extract_date_tag(prior_account_path)\n    files = payload.get(\"files\", {}) or {}\n    positions_path = None\n    if files.get(\"positions_dated\"):\n        candidate = Path(str(files.get(\"positions_dated\")))\n        positions_path = candidate if candidate.exists() else None\n    if positions_path is None:\n        fallback = report_path(REPORT_DIR, \"positions_dated\", profile_slug=profile_slug, date_tag=source_date_tag)\n        positions_path = fallback if fallback.exists() else None\n\n    positions_df = load_positions_snapshot(positions_path)\n    available_cash = parse_float(payload.get(\"cash\"), initial_cash)\n    account_nav = parse_float(payload.get(\"nav\"), available_cash)\n    if available_cash <= 0:\n        available_cash = max(account_nav, initial_cash)\n    if account_nav <= 0:\n        account_nav = max(available_cash, initial_cash)\n\n    return {\n        \"available_cash\": available_cash,\n        \"account_nav\": account_nav,\n        \"positions_df\": positions_df,\n        \"source\": \"prior_account_snapshot\",\n        \"source_date_tag\": source_date_tag,\n        \"source_file\": str(prior_account_path),\n    }\n\n\ndef resolve_tickets_path(date_tag: str, tickets_arg: str) -> Path:\n    if tickets_arg:\n        path = resolve_path(tickets_arg)\n        if not path.exists():\n            raise FileNotFoundError(f\"未找到指定票据文件: {path}\")\n        return path\n    preferred = REPORT_DIR / f\"paper_signal_tickets_{date_tag}.csv\"\n    if preferred.exists():\n        return preferred\n    dated = REPORT_DIR / f\"stock_signal_tickets_live_{date_tag}.csv\"\n    if dated.exists():\n        return dated\n    legacy = REPORT_DIR / f\"stock_signal_tickets_{date_tag}.csv\"\n    if legacy.exists():\n        return legacy\n    raise FileNotFoundError(f\"缺少指定日期的票据文件: {dated}\")","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774842711215}}
{"type":"message","id":"6c80df73","parentId":"3e8036ed","timestamp":"2026-03-30T03:52:18.613Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a complete picture. The `state` dict from `resolve_pretrade_state` contains `available_cash`, `account_nav`, `positions_df`, but NOT the paper account's drawdown.\n\nThe paper account's drawdown is in `paper_aggressive_account_v1_latest.json` which has `drawdown_pct`.\n\nThe fix should be:\n1. In `materialize_profile_signal_chain`, instead of using `runtime_metrics.get(\"strategy_max_dd_pct\")` (which is the live strategy's backtest drawdown), we should use the paper account's actual drawdown from the prior account snapshot.\n\n\n2. Since `state` already contains the prior account payload, I can extract `drawdown_pct` directly from it and swap it into the `--strategy-max-dd-pct` parameter in the apply command.\n\nThe tricky part is that this parameter name suggests it's for the live strategy's drawdown, but for paper trading it should use the paper account's drawdown instead. The cleanest solution is to pull `drawdown_pct` from the prior account JSON (which gives the historical peak-to-current drawdown) rather than recalculating it, since that's what the guard is actually checking against. The core issue is that the paper trading pipeline is using the live system's drawdown threshold (24.52%) instead of its own (0.39%), when it should be checking the paper account's actual realized performance. I need to either extract the drawdown directly from `prior_account_payload` or load it from the account JSON, then use that value in `apply_risk_to_merged_signals.py` to replace the live system's metric.\n\nThe simplest approach is to load the prior account file in `resolve_pretrade_state`, pull the `drawdown_pct` field, and pass it through to where it's needed. Since `drawdown_pct` is already tracked in the account JSON as the running maximum drawdown from peak NAV, that should be the right metric to use here.\n\nNow I need to trace through the `apply_risk_to_merged_signals.py` call chain to understand what fields are being passed around and where exactly the fix should go. The `state` dict already has the account payload loaded, so I just need to pass the drawdown value down to `materialize_profile_signal_chain` where the signal application happens. I should modify `resolve_pretrade_state` to include the `drawdown_pct` in the state it returns, then use that value instead of the live strategy's drawdown when building the `apply_cmd` in `materialize_profile_signal_chain`.\n\nBut I'm realizing there's a timing issue here—the `state` is resolved at the start of the day using the prior day's account snapshot, so I need to think through whether using the prior day's drawdown is actually the right metric to use in this context.\n\nLooking at the `paper_aggressive_account_v1_20260327.json`, the drawdown shows as -0.39%, but that's the current day's value, not the peak-to-trough drawdown I need. The real peak-to-trough drawdown for the aggressive strategy is 0.39% from the metrics file, and since the account has been flat since 20260320, that value hasn't changed. So for the halt check, I should be using the account's own drawdown, not the live system's 24.52%.\n\nThe fix needs to go into `resolve_pretrade_state` to properly surface the drawdown information.\n\nActually, I'm realizing there's a cleaner approach—the `state` dict already contains the prior account payload loaded from the JSON file, so I just need to pass `payload.get(\"drawdown_pct\")` down to `materialize_profile_signal_chain` rather than trying to access it differently. Let me check how `materialize_profile_signal_chain` receives and uses this `state` parameter to make sure I wire it up correctly.\n\nLooking at the flow, I can see that `materialize_profile_signal_chain` has access to the account data through `state`, but `drawdown_pct` isn't being extracted and passed through to the `--strategy-max-dd-pct` argument where it's actually needed. The fix is to extract `drawdown_pct` from the prior account payload and use that value instead of pulling it from `runtime_metrics`.\n\nBut there's a deeper issue: the halt logic itself might be flawed. The `decide_mode` function compares `strategy_max_drawdown_pct` against `target_dd`, and if paper trading should use its own drawdown rather than the live strategy's, then the entire halt condition could be triggering incorrectly for paper accounts.\n\nLooking at the threshold configuration, `paper_live_trading_aggressive_v1.json` sets `max_drawdown_max_pct: 25.0`, but the actual halt is triggering at 10% instead. This 10% must be hardcoded somewhere in the risk engine logic, which means I need to trace through `apply_risk_to_merged_signals.py` to find where this threshold is actually being enforced.","thinkingSignature":"ab292d1b50e8985f7c7139aaf448c678b54c0072b28dea4956305e976294419c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0to0zgs2zkk6_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '240,350p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/apply_risk_to_merged_signals.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":54438,"output":1104,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":80562,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774842711231,"responseId":"0619265700264e59b73cb3f952a5bc90"}}
