{"type":"message","id":"62aed6f0","parentId":"54629e68","timestamp":"2026-03-30T03:53:02.494Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, the field is `drawdown_pct` in the account JSON.\n\nNow let me also check whether `resolve_pretrade_state` has the `payload` variable available when returning initial capital case. Let me trace through.\n\nIn `resolve_pretrade_state`:\n- If `date_tag <= start_date_tag`: returns initial capital dict (no `drawdown_pct`)\n- If `prior_account_path is None`: returns initial capital fallback dict (no `drawdown_pct`)\n- Otherwise: loads `payload` from `prior_account_path` and returns data including `payload.get(\"drawdown_pct\")`\n\nSo for initial capital / fallback cases, `drawdown_pct` won't be in `state`. In `materialize_profile_signal_chain`, I'll use `state.get(\"drawdown_pct\", 0.0)` as a safe fallback.\n\n\nNow I'll implement the fix by modifying both functions to handle the drawdown calculation appropriately.","thinkingSignature":"95d4cb23ab9860d570a13c7f74b905e0542204a890bad7b2d15eb7d0c18dfd71"},{"type":"text","text":"根因已完全摸清。现在动手修。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_5l43hbcekhyr_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '530,580p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/prepare_paper_orders_v1.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58618,"output":263,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83901,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774842774619,"responseId":"0619269791d66be8d9fd7ec34dcfbb88"}}
{"type":"message","id":"931039de","parentId":"62aed6f0","timestamp":"2026-03-30T03:53:02.605Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_5l43hbcekhyr_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def resolve_pretrade_state(paper_cfg: dict[str, Any], date_tag: str) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    profile_slug = profile_slug_from_config(paper_cfg)\n    initial_cash = parse_float(paper_cfg.get(\"initial_cash\"), 0.0)\n    start_date_tag = parse_optional_date_tag(paper_cfg.get(\"start_date_tag\", \"\"))\n    if initial_cash <= 0:\n        raise ValueError(\"paper trading config 的 initial_cash 必须大于 0\")\n\n    if start_date_tag and date_tag <= start_date_tag:\n        return {\n            \"available_cash\": initial_cash,\n            \"account_nav\": initial_cash,\n            \"positions_df\": pd.DataFrame(columns=[\"symbol\", \"quantity\", \"cost_price\"]),\n            \"source\": \"initial_capital\",\n            \"source_date_tag\": \"\",\n        }\n\n    prior_account_path = find_latest_prior_account(REPORT_DIR, date_tag, profile_slug=profile_slug)\n    if prior_account_path is None:\n        return {\n            \"available_cash\": initial_cash,\n            \"account_nav\": initial_cash,\n            \"positions_df\": pd.DataFrame(columns=[\"symbol\", \"quantity\", \"cost_price\"]),\n            \"source\": \"initial_capital_fallback\",\n            \"source_date_tag\": \"\",\n        }\n\n    payload = load_json(prior_account_path)\n    source_date_tag = extract_date_tag(prior_account_path)\n    files = payload.get(\"files\", {}) or {}\n    positions_path = None\n    if files.get(\"positions_dated\"):\n        candidate = Path(str(files.get(\"positions_dated\")))\n        positions_path = candidate if candidate.exists() else None\n    if positions_path is None:\n        fallback = report_path(REPORT_DIR, \"positions_dated\", profile_slug=profile_slug, date_tag=source_date_tag)\n        positions_path = fallback if fallback.exists() else None\n\n    positions_df = load_positions_snapshot(positions_path)\n    available_cash = parse_float(payload.get(\"cash\"), initial_cash)\n    account_nav = parse_float(payload.get(\"nav\"), available_cash)\n    if available_cash <= 0:\n        available_cash = max(account_nav, initial_cash)\n    if account_nav <= 0:\n        account_nav = max(available_cash, initial_cash)\n\n    return {\n        \"available_cash\": available_cash,\n        \"account_nav\": account_nav,\n        \"positions_df\": positions_df,\n        \"source\": \"prior_account_snapshot\",\n        \"source_date_tag\": source_date_tag,"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":31,"aggregated":"def resolve_pretrade_state(paper_cfg: dict[str, Any], date_tag: str) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    profile_slug = profile_slug_from_config(paper_cfg)\n    initial_cash = parse_float(paper_cfg.get(\"initial_cash\"), 0.0)\n    start_date_tag = parse_optional_date_tag(paper_cfg.get(\"start_date_tag\", \"\"))\n    if initial_cash <= 0:\n        raise ValueError(\"paper trading config 的 initial_cash 必须大于 0\")\n\n    if start_date_tag and date_tag <= start_date_tag:\n        return {\n            \"available_cash\": initial_cash,\n            \"account_nav\": initial_cash,\n            \"positions_df\": pd.DataFrame(columns=[\"symbol\", \"quantity\", \"cost_price\"]),\n            \"source\": \"initial_capital\",\n            \"source_date_tag\": \"\",\n        }\n\n    prior_account_path = find_latest_prior_account(REPORT_DIR, date_tag, profile_slug=profile_slug)\n    if prior_account_path is None:\n        return {\n            \"available_cash\": initial_cash,\n            \"account_nav\": initial_cash,\n            \"positions_df\": pd.DataFrame(columns=[\"symbol\", \"quantity\", \"cost_price\"]),\n            \"source\": \"initial_capital_fallback\",\n            \"source_date_tag\": \"\",\n        }\n\n    payload = load_json(prior_account_path)\n    source_date_tag = extract_date_tag(prior_account_path)\n    files = payload.get(\"files\", {}) or {}\n    positions_path = None\n    if files.get(\"positions_dated\"):\n        candidate = Path(str(files.get(\"positions_dated\")))\n        positions_path = candidate if candidate.exists() else None\n    if positions_path is None:\n        fallback = report_path(REPORT_DIR, \"positions_dated\", profile_slug=profile_slug, date_tag=source_date_tag)\n        positions_path = fallback if fallback.exists() else None\n\n    positions_df = load_positions_snapshot(positions_path)\n    available_cash = parse_float(payload.get(\"cash\"), initial_cash)\n    account_nav = parse_float(payload.get(\"nav\"), available_cash)\n    if available_cash <= 0:\n        available_cash = max(account_nav, initial_cash)\n    if account_nav <= 0:\n        account_nav = max(available_cash, initial_cash)\n\n    return {\n        \"available_cash\": available_cash,\n        \"account_nav\": account_nav,\n        \"positions_df\": positions_df,\n        \"source\": \"prior_account_snapshot\",\n        \"source_date_tag\": source_date_tag,","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774842782589}}
