{"type":"message","id":"ee331076","parentId":"c926bedb","timestamp":"2026-03-30T03:54:13.377Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good, `apply_risk_to_signals.py` is not called by any other script in this codebase. It's a standalone script. So the fix in `prepare_paper_orders_v1.py` is the only place that needs fixing.\n\nNow let me also verify my changes didn't introduce any syntax errors:","thinkingSignature":"dadc40ff60ff0a2ac36a445e38afed29f5ff9d79ddb20e3b34ddeecad770a402"},{"type":"text","text":"没有其他调用方。现在验证语法正确：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_c2ro21tsv7kv_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -m py_compile /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/prepare_paper_orders_v1.py && echo \"语法OK\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":63052,"output":135,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88207,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774842849451,"responseId":"061926e14385c958f599dd760b24adbb"}}
