{"type":"message","id":"e16fa3c7","parentId":"cb6f5ff1","timestamp":"2026-03-30T03:56:00.246Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_rxpff7ymlmt2_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def decide_mode(\n    live_payload: dict[str, Any],\n    config: dict[str, Any],\n    index_ret_pct: float,\n    market_breadth: float | None,\n    *,\n    date_tag: str = \"\",\n    style_snapshot: dict[str, Any] | None = None,\n) -> RuntimeState:\n    combo = live_payload.get(\"combo_v1\", {})\n    max_dd = parse_float(combo.get(\"max_drawdown_pct\"), 0.0)\n    sharpe = parse_float(combo.get(\"sharpe\"), 0.0)\n    target_dd = parse_float((config.get(\"targets\") or {}).get(\"max_drawdown_max_pct\"), 25.0)\n    runtime_date_tag = parse_date_tag(date_tag) if str(date_tag or \"\").strip() else datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n    if style_snapshot is None:\n        style_snapshot = load_style_rotation_snapshot(config, cutoff_date_key=parse_int(runtime_date_tag, 0))\n\n    runtime_risk_cfg = build_runtime_risk_config(config=config, target_dd=target_dd)\n    engine = RiskEngine(runtime_risk_cfg)\n    decision = engine.evaluate_runtime_state(\n        RiskContext(\n            trade_date=f\"{runtime_date_tag[0:4]}-{runtime_date_tag[4:6]}-{runtime_date_tag[6:8]}\",\n            market_breadth=market_breadth,\n            index_ret_pct=index_ret_pct,\n            strategy_max_drawdown_pct=max_dd,\n            strategy_sharpe=sharpe,\n            style_smallcap_short_return_pct=parse_optional_float(style_snapshot.get(\"smallcap_short_return_pct\")),\n            style_smallcap_medium_return_pct=parse_optional_float(style_snapshot.get(\"smallcap_medium_return_pct\")),\n            style_short_excess_pct=parse_optional_float(style_snapshot.get(\"short_excess_pct\")),\n            style_medium_excess_pct=parse_optional_float(style_snapshot.get(\"medium_excess_pct\")),\n        )\n    )\n\n    halt_reason = decision.reason\n    if decision.reasons:\n        first = decision.reasons[0]\n        if first.startswith(\"index_ret_pct\"):\n            idx_th = runtime_risk_cfg.index_halt_threshold_pct\n            halt_reason = f\"index_guard触发: 中证2000单日{index_ret_pct:.2f}% <= {idx_th:.2f}%\"\n        elif first.startswith(\"market_breadth\"):\n            breadth_riskoff, breadth_hard_stop = resolve_breadth_thresholds(config)\n            if decision.hard_stop and breadth_hard_stop is not None:\n                halt_reason = f\"market_breadth触发硬停: {market_breadth:.3f} <= {breadth_hard_stop:.3f}\"\n            elif breadth_riskoff is not None:\n                halt_reason = f\"market_breadth触发风险收缩: {market_breadth:.3f} <= {breadth_riskoff:.3f}\"\n        elif first.startswith(\"strategy_max_drawdown_pct\"):\n            halt_reason = f\"组合历史回撤{max_dd:.2f}% >= 目标上限{target_dd:.2f}%\"\n        elif first.startswith(\"strategy_sharpe\"):\n            sharpe_th = runtime_risk_cfg.strategy_sharpe_cautious_threshold\n            halt_reason = f\"Sharpe偏低({sharpe:.3f} < {sharpe_th:.3f})，降低新增仓位\"\n        elif first == \"style_rotation_hard_stop\":\n            halt_reason = (\n                \"风格切换硬停: \"\n                f\"{style_snapshot.get('smallcap_index', 'ZZ2000')}相对\"\n                f\"{style_snapshot.get('broad_index', 'HS300')}\"\n                f\"{int(style_snapshot.get('short_window', 5))}日超额=\"\n                f\"{parse_float(style_snapshot.get('short_excess_pct'), 0.0):.2f}% / \"\n                f\"{int(style_snapshot.get('medium_window', 20))}日超额=\"\n                f\"{parse_float(style_snapshot.get('medium_excess_pct'), 0.0):.2f}%\"\n            )\n        elif first == \"style_rotation_riskoff\":\n            halt_reason = (\n                \"风格切换收缩: \"\n                f\"{style_snapshot.get('smallcap_index', 'ZZ2000')}相对\"\n                f\"{style_snapshot.get('broad_index', 'HS300')}\"\n                f\"{int(style_snapshot.get('short_window', 5))}日超额=\"\n                f\"{parse_float(style_snapshot.get('short_excess_pct'), 0.0):.2f}% / \"\n                f\"{int(style_snapshot.get('medium_window', 20))}日超额=\"\n                f\"{parse_float(style_snapshot.get('medium_excess_pct'), 0.0):.2f}%\"\n            )\n        elif first == \"manual_hard_stop\":\n            halt_reason = \"人工硬停已触发\"\n        elif first == \"manual_risk_off\":\n            halt_reason = \"人工风险收缩已触发\""}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":31,"aggregated":"def decide_mode(\n    live_payload: dict[str, Any],\n    config: dict[str, Any],\n    index_ret_pct: float,\n    market_breadth: float | None,\n    *,\n    date_tag: str = \"\",\n    style_snapshot: dict[str, Any] | None = None,\n) -> RuntimeState:\n    combo = live_payload.get(\"combo_v1\", {})\n    max_dd = parse_float(combo.get(\"max_drawdown_pct\"), 0.0)\n    sharpe = parse_float(combo.get(\"sharpe\"), 0.0)\n    target_dd = parse_float((config.get(\"targets\") or {}).get(\"max_drawdown_max_pct\"), 25.0)\n    runtime_date_tag = parse_date_tag(date_tag) if str(date_tag or \"\").strip() else datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y%m%d\")\n    if style_snapshot is None:\n        style_snapshot = load_style_rotation_snapshot(config, cutoff_date_key=parse_int(runtime_date_tag, 0))\n\n    runtime_risk_cfg = build_runtime_risk_config(config=config, target_dd=target_dd)\n    engine = RiskEngine(runtime_risk_cfg)\n    decision = engine.evaluate_runtime_state(\n        RiskContext(\n            trade_date=f\"{runtime_date_tag[0:4]}-{runtime_date_tag[4:6]}-{runtime_date_tag[6:8]}\",\n            market_breadth=market_breadth,\n            index_ret_pct=index_ret_pct,\n            strategy_max_drawdown_pct=max_dd,\n            strategy_sharpe=sharpe,\n            style_smallcap_short_return_pct=parse_optional_float(style_snapshot.get(\"smallcap_short_return_pct\")),\n            style_smallcap_medium_return_pct=parse_optional_float(style_snapshot.get(\"smallcap_medium_return_pct\")),\n            style_short_excess_pct=parse_optional_float(style_snapshot.get(\"short_excess_pct\")),\n            style_medium_excess_pct=parse_optional_float(style_snapshot.get(\"medium_excess_pct\")),\n        )\n    )\n\n    halt_reason = decision.reason\n    if decision.reasons:\n        first = decision.reasons[0]\n        if first.startswith(\"index_ret_pct\"):\n            idx_th = runtime_risk_cfg.index_halt_threshold_pct\n            halt_reason = f\"index_guard触发: 中证2000单日{index_ret_pct:.2f}% <= {idx_th:.2f}%\"\n        elif first.startswith(\"market_breadth\"):\n            breadth_riskoff, breadth_hard_stop = resolve_breadth_thresholds(config)\n            if decision.hard_stop and breadth_hard_stop is not None:\n                halt_reason = f\"market_breadth触发硬停: {market_breadth:.3f} <= {breadth_hard_stop:.3f}\"\n            elif breadth_riskoff is not None:\n                halt_reason = f\"market_breadth触发风险收缩: {market_breadth:.3f} <= {breadth_riskoff:.3f}\"\n        elif first.startswith(\"strategy_max_drawdown_pct\"):\n            halt_reason = f\"组合历史回撤{max_dd:.2f}% >= 目标上限{target_dd:.2f}%\"\n        elif first.startswith(\"strategy_sharpe\"):\n            sharpe_th = runtime_risk_cfg.strategy_sharpe_cautious_threshold\n            halt_reason = f\"Sharpe偏低({sharpe:.3f} < {sharpe_th:.3f})，降低新增仓位\"\n        elif first == \"style_rotation_hard_stop\":\n            halt_reason = (\n                \"风格切换硬停: \"\n                f\"{style_snapshot.get('smallcap_index', 'ZZ2000')}相对\"\n                f\"{style_snapshot.get('broad_index', 'HS300')}\"\n                f\"{int(style_snapshot.get('short_window', 5))}日超额=\"\n                f\"{parse_float(style_snapshot.get('short_excess_pct'), 0.0):.2f}% / \"\n                f\"{int(style_snapshot.get('medium_window', 20))}日超额=\"\n                f\"{parse_float(style_snapshot.get('medium_excess_pct'), 0.0):.2f}%\"\n            )\n        elif first == \"style_rotation_riskoff\":\n            halt_reason = (\n                \"风格切换收缩: \"\n                f\"{style_snapshot.get('smallcap_index', 'ZZ2000')}相对\"\n                f\"{style_snapshot.get('broad_index', 'HS300')}\"\n                f\"{int(style_snapshot.get('short_window', 5))}日超额=\"\n                f\"{parse_float(style_snapshot.get('short_excess_pct'), 0.0):.2f}% / \"\n                f\"{int(style_snapshot.get('medium_window', 20))}日超额=\"\n                f\"{parse_float(style_snapshot.get('medium_excess_pct'), 0.0):.2f}%\"\n            )\n        elif first == \"manual_hard_stop\":\n            halt_reason = \"人工硬停已触发\"\n        elif first == \"manual_risk_off\":\n            halt_reason = \"人工风险收缩已触发\"","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774842960229}}
{"type":"message","id":"df8806e3","parentId":"e16fa3c7","timestamp":"2026-03-30T03:56:07.688Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I can see the complete picture. In `decide_mode`, the `halt_reason` is set based on the first reason in `decision.reasons`. The `decision` comes from `engine.evaluate_runtime_state()`.\n\nLooking at `risk_engine.py` lines 166-170:\n```python\nmax_dd = context.strategy_max_drawdown_pct\nmax_dd_th = self.config.strategy_max_drawdown_riskoff_pct\nif max_dd_th is not None and max_dd is not None and max_dd >= max_dd_th:\n    risk_off = True\n    reasons.append(self._fmt_threshold_trigger(\"strategy_max_drawdown_pct\", max_dd, max_dd_th, \">=\"))\n\n\n```\n\nThe drawdown check only sets `risk_off = True`, not `hard_stop = True`, so it wouldn't trigger a halt. But the gate reason string `strategy_max_drawdown_pct(24.5200) >= 10.0000` suggests there's a hard stop check happening somewhere else. Looking at `risk_engine.py` around line 180, there's a separate hard_stop condition that must be where this is actually being enforced.\n\n```","thinkingSignature":"0472de220fb568779a8d4e4635f70dd49dca683df845384654a1503b4c88bcf2"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2tqiomjepzuo_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '178,210p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/risk/risk_engine.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":73466,"output":301,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":98787,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774842960246,"responseId":"06192750ad9839a4455f0041c294894c"}}
