{"type":"message","id":"46778599","parentId":"46365ce5","timestamp":"2026-03-30T03:57:45.400Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The diff looks correct. Now let me commit just this file.","thinkingSignature":"31a440200925c0ca78958f8aa597700eca30133090be035702e2b4ef18dd2e57"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_xx88az8a9w9k_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace && git add quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/prepare_paper_orders_v1.py && git commit -m \"fix(paper): 用纸纸账户实际回撤替换live combo回撤\n\n纸纸账户的风控层之前引用了 live combo 的历史回测回撤（24.52%），\n导致 aggressive 策略的 --strategy-max-dd-pct 被错误设置，\n触发了组合级熔断 halt（halt_reason=24.52% >= 10%硬止损线），\n所有买单被静默拒绝，journal 无记录，触发 NO_JOURNAL_WITH_PLANNED_ORDERS 告警。\n\n修复：\n- resolve_pretrade_state() 三条返回路径均增加 drawdown_pct\n  （初始资金/降级=0.0，有历史账户=payload.drawdown_pct）\n- materialize_profile_signal_chain() 的 --strategy-max-dd-pct 参数\n  改用 state[\"drawdown_pct\"]（纸纸账户实际运行回撤），\n  不再引用 runtime_metrics[\"strategy_max_dd_pct\"]（live combo 回测回撤）\n\n影响范围：仅 paper trading 链路，live 实盘不受影响。\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":87404,"output":294,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":112718,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774843052838,"responseId":"061927ad22069931e7448ef27b985697"}}
