{"type":"message","id":"427214d3","parentId":"f13a74cf","timestamp":"2026-03-30T03:57:56.445Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The commit is done. Let me now provide a clean summary to the user.","thinkingSignature":"5d89a2b80b3cdafff4e2b0f0be4635e4a88d88cb056263b071e097de27ef9936"},{"type":"text","text":"修改完成，已提交。总结一下修复内容：\n\n---\n\n## 根因\n\n纸纸账户风控链路里，`--strategy-max-dd-pct` 参数**错误地引用了 live combo 的历史回测回撤**（24.52%），而不是纸纸账户的实际运行回撤（0.39%）。\n\n这条错误数据一路传导：\n1. `decide_mode()` → `halt_reason = \"组合历史回撤24.52% >= 目标上限10.0%\"` → `halt_new_buy = True`\n2. `size_orders()` → `blocked_buy_halt += 1`，所有订单 `risk_gate = \"blocked\"`\n3. 守卫检测到 journal 无记录 + 有计划订单 → RED halt\n\n## 修复（`prepare_paper_orders_v1.py`）\n\n| 位置 | 修复内容 |\n|------|---------|\n| `resolve_pretrade_state()` 三条返回路径 | 增加 `drawdown_pct` 字段（初始资金=0.0，有历史账户=纸纸账户真实回撤） |\n| `materialize_profile_signal_chain()` `--strategy-max-dd-pct` 参数 | `state[\"drawdown_pct\"]`（纸纸实际）替换 `runtime_metrics[\"strategy_max_dd_pct\"]`（live combo 回测） |\n\n修复后，aggressive 纸纸账户的 `--strategy-max-dd-pct` = **0.39%**，不会触发 10% 的 halt 阈值，订单正常执行。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":87753,"output":330,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113103,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774843065779,"responseId":"061927b9e42feddd9210b402b3bc9ced"}}
