{"type":"message","id":"8a1a39ba","parentId":"c2425f9d","timestamp":"2026-03-30T04:10:34.346Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"There's an `exit_engine.py` file. Let me read it.","thinkingSignature":"5e5ce33261e7f9805612485d30c92033bf706ea08d7ee0db14f9b0d1c4d44196"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_o7uktlj1qmsn_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/risk/exit_engine.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":84735,"output":65,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":109820,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774843827841,"responseId":"06192ab49c69aaa801345a0a26293eb5"}}
{"type":"message","id":"d9cd5096","parentId":"8a1a39ba","timestamp":"2026-03-30T04:10:34.493Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_o7uktlj1qmsn_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"from __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nimport math\nimport re\nfrom collections import deque\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nimport pandas as pd\n\nDEFAULT_PRICE_HISTORY_PATH = Path(\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/data/a_stock_history.csv\")\n\nBUY_SIDES = {\"BUY\", \"B\", \"LONG\", \"买\"}\n\n\ndef normalize_ts_code(value: Any) -> str:\n    text = str(value or \"\").strip().upper()\n    if not text or text == \"NAN\":\n        return \"\"\n    if text.endswith(\".XSHG\"):\n        return f\"{text[:-5]}.SH\"\n    if text.endswith(\".XSHE\"):\n        return f\"{text[:-5]}.SZ\"\n    if text.endswith((\".SH\", \".SZ\", \".BJ\", \".HK\")):\n        return text\n    if text.isdigit() and len(text) == 6:\n        if text.startswith((\"600\", \"601\", \"603\", \"605\", \"688\")):\n            return f\"{text}.SH\"\n        if text.startswith((\"000\", \"001\", \"002\", \"003\", \"300\", \"301\")):\n            return f\"{text}.SZ\"\n    return text\n\n\ndef is_a_share_stock(ts_code: str) -> bool:\n    code = normalize_ts_code(ts_code)\n    if \".\" not in code:\n        return False\n    symbol, market = code.split(\".\", 1)\n    if market == \"SH\":\n        return symbol.startswith((\"600\", \"601\", \"603\", \"605\", \"688\"))\n    if market == \"SZ\":\n        return symbol.startswith((\"000\", \"001\", \"002\", \"003\", \"300\", \"301\"))\n    return False\n\n\ndef parse_float(value: Any, default: float = 0.0) -> float:\n    try:\n        return float(str(value).replace(\",\", \"\").strip())\n    except Exception:\n        return default\n\n\ndef parse_optional_float(value: Any) -> float | None:\n    if value is None:\n        return None\n    text = str(value).replace(\",\", \"\").strip()\n    if not text or text.lower() == \"none\":\n        return None\n    try:\n        return float(text)\n    except Exception:\n        return None\n\n\ndef parse_int(value: Any, default: int = 0) -> int:\n    try:\n        return int(float(str(value).replace(\",\", \"\").strip()))\n    except Exception:\n        return default\n\n\ndef pct_change(base: float, current: float) -> float:\n    if base <= 0 or current <= 0:\n        return 0.0\n    return (current / base - 1.0) * 100.0\n\n\ndef clamp(value: float, lower: float, upper: float) -> float:\n    return max(lower, min(upper, value))\n\n\ndef parse_date_tag(value: Any) -> int:\n    text = str(value or \"\").strip()\n    digits = re.sub(r\"\\D\", \"\", text)\n    if len(digits) >= 8:\n        return parse_int(digits[:8], 0)\n    return 0\n\n\ndef latest_report_file(report_dir: Path, patterns: list[str], cutoff_date: int = 0) -> Path | None:\n    def sort_key(path: Path) -> tuple[int, float, str]:\n        return (parse_date_tag(path.stem), path.stat().st_mtime, path.name)\n\n    files: list[Path] = []\n    for pattern in patterns:\n        files.extend(report_dir.glob(pattern))\n    if not files:\n        return None\n    if cutoff_date > 0:\n        eligible = [path for path in files if parse_date_tag(path.stem) <= 0 or parse_date_tag(path.stem) <= cutoff_date]\n        if not eligible:\n            return None\n        files = eligible\n    return max(files, key=sort_key)\n\n\ndef resolve_path(value: Any, *, base_dir: Path) -> Path | None:\n    text = str(value or \"\").strip()\n    if not text:\n        return None\n    path = Path(text)\n    if not path.is_absolute():\n        path = (base_dir / path).resolve()\n    return path\n\n\ndef first_existing_column(frame: pd.DataFrame, candidates: list[str]) -> str:\n    for candidate in candidates:\n        if candidate in frame.columns:\n            return candidate\n    return \"\"\n\n\ndef load_holdings(path: Path | None) -> pd.DataFrame:\n    columns = [\"ts_code\", \"qty\", \"cost_price\", \"name\"]\n    if path is None or not path.exists():\n        return pd.DataFrame(columns=columns)\n\n    frame = pd.read_csv(path)\n    if frame.empty:\n        return pd.DataFrame(columns=columns)\n\n    code_col = first_existing_column(frame, [\"ts_code\", \"symbol\", \"security\", \"code\"])\n    qty_col = first_existing_column(frame, [\"qty\", \"quantity\", \"shares\", \"position\", \"current_qty\"])\n    cost_col = first_existing_column(frame, [\"cost_price\", \"cost\", \"avg_cost\", \"hold_cost\", \"price_cost\"])\n    name_col = first_existing_column(frame, [\"name\", \"security_name\"])\n    if not code_col or not qty_col:\n        return pd.DataFrame(columns=columns)\n\n    out = pd.DataFrame()\n    out[\"ts_code\"] = frame[code_col].map(normalize_ts_code)\n    out[\"qty\"] = pd.to_numeric(frame[qty_col], errors=\"coerce\").fillna(0).astype(int)\n    out[\"cost_price\"] = (\n        pd.to_numeric(frame[cost_col], errors=\"coerce\").fillna(0.0) if cost_col else 0.0\n    )\n    out[\"name\"] = frame[name_col].fillna(\"\").astype(str) if name_col else \"\"\n    out = out[(out[\"qty\"] > 0) & out[\"ts_code\"].map(is_a_share_stock)].copy()\n    out = out.drop_duplicates(subset=[\"ts_code\"], keep=\"first\").reset_index(drop=True)\n    return out[columns]\n\n\ndef load_latest_buy_dates(path: Path | None, codes: set[str], cutoff_date: int = 0) -> dict[str, int]:\n    if path is None or not path.exists() or not codes:\n        return {}\n\n    frame = pd.read_csv(path)\n    if frame.empty:\n        return {}\n\n    code_col = first_existing_column(frame, [\"ts_code\", \"symbol\", \"security\", \"code\"])\n    side_col = first_existing_column(frame, [\"side\", \"action\", \"direction\"])\n    date_col = first_existing_column(frame, [\"trade_date\", \"date\", \"biz_date\"])\n    if not code_col or not date_col:\n        return {}\n\n    out = pd.DataFrame()\n    out[\"ts_code\"] = frame[code_col].map(normalize_ts_code)\n    out[\"trade_date\"] = frame[date_col].map(parse_date_tag)\n    if side_col:\n        out[\"side\"] = frame[side_col].fillna(\"\").astype(str).str.upper().str.strip()\n        out = out[out[\"side\"].isin(BUY_SIDES)]\n    out = out[(out[\"trade_date\"] > 0) & out[\"ts_code\"].isin(codes)].copy()\n    if cutoff_date > 0:\n        out = out[out[\"trade_date\"] <= cutoff_date].copy()\n    if out.empty:\n        return {}\n    grouped = out.groupby(\"ts_code\", as_index=False)[\"trade_date\"].max()\n    return dict(zip(grouped[\"ts_code\"], grouped[\"trade_date\"]))\n\n\ndef load_price_snapshot(\n    price_history_path: Path,\n    codes: set[str],\n    entry_dates: dict[str, int],\n    cutoff_date: int = 0,\n) -> tuple[dict[str, float], dict[str, float], int]:\n    latest_close: dict[str, tuple[int, float]] = {}\n    peak_high: dict[str, float] = {code: 0.0 for code in codes}\n    latest_trade_date = 0\n    if not price_history_path.exists() or not codes:\n        return {}, peak_high, latest_trade_date\n\n    for chunk in pd.read_csv(\n        price_history_path,\n        usecols=[\"ts_code\", \"trade_date\", \"high\", \"close\"],\n        chunksize=200000,\n    ):\n        chunk[\"ts_code\"] = chunk[\"ts_code\"].astype(str).str.upper().str.strip()\n        chunk = chunk[chunk[\"ts_code\"].isin(codes)].copy()\n        if chunk.empty:\n            continue\n\n        chunk[\"trade_date\"] = pd.to_numeric(chunk[\"trade_date\"], errors=\"coerce\").fillna(0).astype(int)\n        chunk[\"high\"] = pd.to_numeric(chunk[\"high\"], errors=\"coerce\")\n        chunk[\"close\"] = pd.to_numeric(chunk[\"close\"], errors=\"coerce\")\n        chunk = chunk.dropna(subset=[\"close\"])\n        chunk = chunk[chunk[\"trade_date\"] > 0]\n        if cutoff_date > 0:\n            chunk = chunk[chunk[\"trade_date\"] <= cutoff_date]\n        if chunk.empty:\n            continue\n\n        chunk = chunk.sort_values([\"ts_code\", \"trade_date\"])\n        for row in chunk.itertuples(index=False):\n            code = str(row.ts_code)\n            trade_date = int(row.trade_date)\n            close = parse_float(row.close, 0.0)\n            high = parse_float(row.high, close)\n            latest_trade_date = max(latest_trade_date, trade_date)\n            current = latest_close.get(code)\n            if current is None or trade_date >= current[0]:\n                latest_close[code] = (trade_date, close)\n            entry_date = entry_dates.get(code, 0)\n            if entry_date <= 0 or trade_date >= entry_date:\n                peak_high[code] = max(parse_float(peak_high.get(code), 0.0), high, close)\n\n    close_map = {code: value[1] for code, value in latest_close.items()}\n    return close_map, peak_high, latest_trade_date\n\n\ndef load_latest_ma_snapshot(\n    price_history_path: Path,\n    codes: set[str],\n    window: int,\n    cutoff_date: int = 0,\n) -> dict[str, float]:\n    if not price_history_path.exists() or not codes or window <= 0:\n        return {}\n\n    close_windows: dict[str, deque[float]] = {\n        code: deque(maxlen=max(1, int(window)))\n        for code in codes\n    }\n    for chunk in pd.read_csv(\n        price_history_path,\n        usecols=[\"ts_code\", \"trade_date\", \"close\"],\n        chunksize=200000,\n    ):\n        chunk[\"ts_code\"] = chunk[\"ts_code\"].astype(str).str.upper().str.strip()\n        chunk = chunk[chunk[\"ts_code\"].isin(codes)].copy()\n        if chunk.empty:\n            continue\n\n        chunk[\"trade_date\"] = pd.to_numeric(chunk[\"trade_date\"], errors=\"coerce\").fillna(0).astype(int)\n        chunk[\"close\"] = pd.to_numeric(chunk[\"close\"], errors=\"coerce\")\n        chunk = chunk.dropna(subset=[\"close\"])\n        chunk = chunk[chunk[\"trade_date\"] > 0]\n        if cutoff_date > 0:\n            chunk = chunk[chunk[\"trade_date\"] <= cutoff_date]\n        if chunk.empty:\n            continue\n\n        chunk = chunk.sort_values([\"ts_code\", \"trade_date\"])\n        for row in chunk.itertuples(index=False):\n            code = str(row.ts_code)\n            close = parse_float(row.close, 0.0)\n            if close > 0:\n                close_windows.setdefault(code, deque(maxlen=max(1, int(window)))).append(close)\n\n    ma_map: dict[str, float] = {}\n    for code, values in close_windows.items():\n        if values:\n            ma_map[code] = sum(values) / len(values)\n    return ma_map\n\n\ndef load_peak_state(path: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    if not path.exists():\n        return {\"positions\": {}}\n    try:\n        payload = json.loads(path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n    except Exception:\n        return {\"positions\": {}}\n    if not isinstance(payload, dict):\n        return {\"positions\": {}}\n    positions = payload.get(\"positions\")\n    if not isinstance(positions, dict):\n        payload[\"positions\"] = {}\n    return payload\n\n\ndef save_peak_state(path: Path, state: dict[str, Any]) -> None:\n    path.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    path.write_text(json.dumps(state, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n\n\ndef resolve_exit_config(live_config: dict[str, Any], *, project_root: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    if not isinstance(live_config, dict):\n        live_config = {}\n    defaults: dict[str, Any] = {\n        \"enabled\": True,\n        \"stop_loss_pct\": -5.0,\n        \"stop_loss_soft_pct\": None,\n        \"stop_loss_soft_sell_ratio\": 0.5,\n        \"stop_loss_hard_pct\": None,\n        \"trailing_take_profit_arm_pct\": 8.0,\n        \"trailing_take_profit_drawdown_pct\": 4.0,\n        \"trailing_take_profit_confirm_bars\": 1,\n        \"trailing_take_profit_below_ma_window\": 0,\n        \"mode_cautious_target_exposure\": 0.65,\n        \"mode_halt_target_exposure\": 0.30,\n        \"peak_price_state_path\": \"research/reports/live_exit_peak_state_v1.json\",\n        \"price_history_path\": str(DEFAULT_PRICE_HISTORY_PATH),\n    }\n    block = live_config.get(\"exit_rules\", {}) or {}\n    if isinstance(block, dict):\n        defaults.update({k: v for k, v in block.items() if v not in (None, \"\")})\n    defaults[\"enabled\"] = bool(defaults.get(\"enabled\", True))\n    defaults[\"stop_loss_pct\"] = parse_float(defaults.get(\"stop_loss_pct\"), -5.0)\n    defaults[\"stop_loss_soft_pct\"] = parse_optional_float(defaults.get(\"stop_loss_soft_pct\"))\n    defaults[\"stop_loss_soft_sell_ratio\"] = max(0.0, min(1.0, parse_float(defaults.get(\"stop_loss_soft_sell_ratio\"), 0.5)))\n    defaults[\"stop_loss_hard_pct\"] = parse_optional_float(defaults.get(\"stop_loss_hard_pct\"))\n    for key in [\n        \"trailing_take_profit_arm_pct\",\n        \"trailing_take_profit_drawdown_pct\",\n        \"mode_cautious_target_exposure\",\n        \"mode_halt_target_exposure\",\n    ]:\n        defaults[key] = parse_float(defaults.get(key), parse_float(defaults.get(key), 0.0))\n    defaults[\"trailing_take_profit_confirm_bars\"] = max(\n        1,\n        parse_int(defaults.get(\"trailing_take_profit_confirm_bars\"), 1),\n    )\n    defaults[\"trailing_take_profit_below_ma_window\"] = max(\n        0,\n        parse_int(defaults.get(\"trailing_take_profit_below_ma_window\"), 0),\n    )\n    defaults[\"peak_price_state_path\"] = str(\n        resolve_path(defaults.get(\"peak_price_state_path\"), base_dir=project_root) or \"\"\n    )\n    defaults[\"price_history_path\"] = str(\n        resolve_path(defaults.get(\"price_history_path\"), base_dir=project_root) or DEFAULT_PRICE_HISTORY_PATH\n    )\n    return defaults\n\n\ndef resolve_stop_loss_rules(cfg: dict[str, Any]) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    legacy_pct = parse_optional_float(cfg.get(\"stop_loss_pct\"))\n    soft_pct = parse_optional_float(cfg.get(\"stop_loss_soft_pct\"))\n    hard_pct = parse_optional_float(cfg.get(\"stop_loss_hard_pct\"))\n    soft_sell_ratio = max(0.0, min(1.0, parse_float(cfg.get(\"stop_loss_soft_sell_ratio\"), 0.5)))\n\n    if soft_pct is None and hard_pct is None:\n        return {\n            \"mode\": \"single\",\n            \"single_pct\": legacy_pct if legacy_pct is not None else -5.0,\n            \"soft_pct\": None,\n            \"hard_pct\": None,\n            \"soft_sell_ratio\": 1.0,\n        }\n\n    if soft_pct is None and hard_pct is not None:\n        return {\n            \"mode\": \"single\",\n            \"single_pct\": hard_pct,\n            \"soft_pct\": None,\n            \"hard_pct\": None,\n            \"soft_sell_ratio\": 1.0,\n        }\n\n    if soft_pct is not None and hard_pct is None:\n        hard_pct = legacy_pct if legacy_pct is not None else soft_pct\n\n    ordered = sorted([x for x in [soft_pct, hard_pct] if x is not None], reverse=True)\n    if len(ordered) < 2:\n        return {\n            \"mode\": \"single\",\n            \"single_pct\": ordered[0] if ordered else (legacy_pct if legacy_pct is not None else -5.0),\n            \"soft_pct\": None,\n            \"hard_pct\": None,\n            \"soft_sell_ratio\": 1.0,\n        }\n\n    resolved_soft_pct = ordered[0]\n    resolved_hard_pct = ordered[1]\n    if soft_sell_ratio <= 0.0:\n        return {\n            \"mode\": \"single\",\n            \"single_pct\": resolved_hard_pct,\n            \"soft_pct\": None,\n            \"hard_pct\": None,\n            \"soft_sell_ratio\": 1.0,\n        }\n    if soft_sell_ratio >= 1.0 or resolved_soft_pct <= resolved_hard_pct:\n        return {\n            \"mode\": \"single\",\n            \"single_pct\": resolved_soft_pct,\n            \"soft_pct\": None,\n            \"hard_pct\": None,\n            \"soft_sell_ratio\": 1.0,\n        }\n\n    return {\n        \"mode\": \"dual\",\n        \"single_pct\": None,\n        \"soft_pct\": resolved_soft_pct,\n        \"hard_pct\": resolved_hard_pct,\n        \"soft_sell_ratio\": soft_sell_ratio,\n    }\n\n\ndef compute_partial_exit_qty(qty: int, sell_ratio: float) -> int:\n    if qty <= 0 or sell_ratio <= 0:\n        return 0\n    return min(qty, max(1, int(math.ceil(qty * sell_ratio))))\n\n\ndef resolve_soft_stop_reissue_qty(prev_state: dict[str, Any], current_qty: int, default_reduce_qty: int) -> int:\n    trigger_qty = parse_int(prev_state.get(\"soft_trigger_qty\"), 0)\n    remaining_qty = parse_int(prev_state.get(\"soft_expected_remaining_qty\"), -1)\n    reduce_qty = parse_int(prev_state.get(\"soft_reduce_qty\"), 0)\n\n    if trigger_qty > 0 and current_qty > trigger_qty:\n        return default_reduce_qty\n\n    if remaining_qty < 0:\n        return 0\n    if current_qty <= remaining_qty:\n        return 0\n\n    pending_reduce_qty = current_qty - remaining_qty\n    if reduce_qty > 0:\n        pending_reduce_qty = min(pending_reduce_qty, reduce_qty)\n    return max(0, pending_reduce_qty)\n\n\ndef build_exit_signal_row(\n    *,\n    trade_date: str,\n    ts_code: str,\n    qty: int,\n    ref_price: float,\n    reason: str,\n    exit_type: str,\n    score: float,\n    reduce_score: float | None = None,\n    reduce_rank_reason: str = \"\",\n) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    now_text = datetime.now().astimezone().isoformat()\n    return {\n        \"trade_date\": trade_date,\n        \"ts_code\": ts_code,\n        \"signal_type\": \"SELL\",\n        \"score\": round(score, 6),\n        \"target_weight\": 0.0,\n        \"target_qty\": int(max(0, qty)),\n        \"ref_price\": round(ref_price, 4) if ref_price > 0 else None,\n        \"strategy_id\": \"exit_engine_v1\",\n        \"risk_flag\": \"exit_engine\",\n        \"comment\": reason,\n        \"source_run_id\": f\"exit_engine_v1_{trade_date.replace('-', '')}\",\n        \"generated_at\": now_text,\n        \"approved\": True,\n        \"risk_status\": \"exit\",\n        \"risk_adjustment\": exit_type,\n        \"exit_type\": exit_type,\n        \"exit_reason\": reason,\n        \"reason\": reason,\n        \"reduce_score\": round(parse_float(reduce_score, 0.0), 6) if reduce_score is not None else None,\n        \"reduce_rank_reason\": reduce_rank_reason,\n    }\n\n\ndef compute_mode_de_risk_reduce_score(\n    *,\n    in_candidates: bool,\n    return_pct: float,\n    buy_score: float,\n) -> tuple[float, str]:\n    non_candidate_bonus = 10.0 if not in_candidates else 0.0\n    return_component = clamp(-parse_float(return_pct, 0.0) / 5.0, -2.0, 2.0)\n    weak_buy_component = 0.5 * (1.0 - clamp(parse_float(buy_score, 0.0), 0.0, 1.0))\n    total = non_candidate_bonus + return_component + weak_buy_component\n    detail = (\n        f\"non_candidate_bonus={non_candidate_bonus:.2f};\"\n        f\"return_component={return_component:.2f};\"\n        f\"weak_buy_component={weak_buy_component:.2f}\"\n    )\n    return round(total, 6), detail\n\n\ndef generate_exit_signals(\n    *,\n    trade_date: str,\n    account_nav: float,\n    mode: str,\n    live_config: dict[str, Any],\n    project_root: Path,\n    report_dir: Path,\n    holdings_path: Path | None,\n    trade_history_path: Path | None = None,\n    lot_size: int = 100,\n    candidate_codes: set[str] | None = None,\n    buy_score_map: dict[str, float] | None = None,\n) -> tuple[pd.DataFrame, dict[str, Any]]:\n    cfg = resolve_exit_config(live_config, project_root=project_root)\n    summary: dict[str, Any] = {\n        \"enabled\": bool(cfg.get(\"enabled\", True)),\n        \"holdings_path\": \"\",\n        \"trade_history_path\": \"\",\n        \"holdings_count\": 0,\n        \"price_hit_count\": 0,\n        \"stop_loss_count\": 0,\n        \"stop_loss_reduce_count\": 0,\n        \"stop_loss_hard_count\": 0,\n        \"trailing_stop_count\": 0,\n        \"de_risk_count\": 0,\n        \"mode\": mode,\n        \"target_exposure\": None,\n        \"current_exposure\": None,\n        \"post_exit_exposure\": None,\n        \"state_path\": str(cfg.get(\"peak_price_state_path\", \"\")),\n        \"de_risk_score_rule\": (\n            \"reduce_score=10*(非候选股) + clip(-return_pct/5,-2,2) + 0.5*(1-clamp(buy_score,0,1))\"\n        ),\n    }\n    empty = pd.DataFrame()\n    if not bool(cfg.get(\"enabled\", True)):\n        summary[\"reason\"] = \"disabled\"\n        return empty, summary\n    cutoff_date = parse_date_tag(trade_date)\n\n    holdings_file = holdings_path\n    if holdings_file is None:\n        holdings_file = latest_report_file(\n            report_dir,\n            [\"broker_api_holdings_*.csv\", \"ths_app_holdings_*.csv\", \"account_holdings_*.csv\"],\n            cutoff_date=cutoff_date,\n        )\n    if holdings_file is None or not holdings_file.exists():\n        summary[\"reason\"] = \"holdings_not_found\"\n        return empty, summary\n    summary[\"holdings_path\"] = str(holdings_file)\n\n    holdings = load_holdings(holdings_file)\n    summary[\"holdings_count\"] = int(len(holdings))\n    if holdings.empty:\n        summary[\"reason\"] = \"holdings_empty\"\n        return empty, summary\n\n    if trade_history_path is None:\n        trade_history_path = latest_report_file(\n            report_dir,\n            [\"ths_app_trades_*.csv\", \"ths_trades_*.csv\"],\n            cutoff_date=cutoff_date,\n        )\n    if trade_history_path is not None and trade_history_path.exists():\n        summary[\"trade_history_path\"] = str(trade_history_path)\n\n    codes = set(holdings[\"ts_code\"].tolist())\n    entry_dates = load_latest_buy_dates(trade_history_path, codes, cutoff_date=cutoff_date)\n\n    state_path = Path(str(cfg[\"peak_price_state_path\"]))\n    state = load_peak_state(state_path)\n    old_positions = state.get(\"positions\", {}) or {}\n    for code, payload in old_positions.items():\n        if code not in entry_dates and isinstance(payload, dict):\n            entry_date = parse_date_tag(payload.get(\"entry_date\"))\n            if entry_date > 0:\n                entry_dates[code] = entry_date\n\n    close_map, peak_map, latest_trade_date = load_price_snapshot(\n        Path(str(cfg[\"price_history_path\"])),\n        codes,\n        entry_dates,\n        cutoff_date=cutoff_date,\n    )\n    summary[\"price_hit_count\"] = int(sum(1 for code in codes if parse_float(close_map.get(code), 0.0) > 0))\n\n    candidate_codes = {normalize_ts_code(code) for code in (candidate_codes or set()) if normalize_ts_code(code)}\n    buy_score_map = {normalize_ts_code(k): parse_float(v, 0.0) for k, v in (buy_score_map or {}).items()}\n    stop_loss_rules = resolve_stop_loss_rules(cfg)\n    summary[\"stop_loss_mode\"] = str(stop_loss_rules.get(\"mode\", \"single\"))\n    if stop_loss_rules.get(\"mode\") == \"dual\":\n        summary[\"stop_loss_soft_pct\"] = stop_loss_rules.get(\"soft_pct\")\n        summary[\"stop_loss_hard_pct\"] = stop_loss_rules.get(\"hard_pct\")\n        summary[\"stop_loss_soft_sell_ratio\"] = stop_loss_rules.get(\"soft_sell_ratio\")\n    else:\n        summary[\"stop_loss_pct\"] = stop_loss_rules.get(\"single_pct\")\n    arm_pct = parse_float(cfg.get(\"trailing_take_profit_arm_pct\"), 8.0)\n    trailing_dd_pct = abs(parse_float(cfg.get(\"trailing_take_profit_drawdown_pct\"), 4.0))\n    trailing_confirm_bars = max(1, parse_int(cfg.get(\"trailing_take_profit_confirm_bars\"), 1))\n    trailing_below_ma_window = max(0, parse_int(cfg.get(\"trailing_take_profit_below_ma_window\"), 0))\n    summary[\"trailing_take_profit_arm_pct\"] = arm_pct\n    summary[\"trailing_take_profit_drawdown_pct\"] = trailing_dd_pct\n    summary[\"trailing_take_profit_confirm_bars\"] = trailing_confirm_bars\n    summary[\"trailing_take_profit_below_ma_window\"] = trailing_below_ma_window\n    trailing_ma_map = load_latest_ma_snapshot(\n        Path(str(cfg[\"price_history_path\"])),\n        codes,\n        trailing_below_ma_window,\n        cutoff_date=cutoff_date,\n    ) if trailing_below_ma_window > 0 else {}\n    exposure_target_map = {\n        \"normal\": 1.0,\n        \"cautious\": max(0.0, min(1.0, parse_float(cfg.get(\"mode_cautious_target_exposure\"), 0.65))),\n        \"halt\": max(0.0, min(1.0, parse_float(cfg.get(\"mode_halt_target_exposure\"), 0.30))),\n    }\n\n    planned_rows: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n    current_positions: dict[str, dict[str, Any]] = {}\n    holdings_records: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n    for row in holdings.to_dict(orient=\"records\"):\n        code = str(row[\"ts_code\"])\n        qty = parse_int(row.get(\"qty\"), 0)\n        cost_price = parse_float(row.get(\"cost_price\"), 0.0)\n        ref_price = parse_float(close_map.get(code), 0.0)\n        prev_state = old_positions.get(code, {}) if isinstance(old_positions.get(code), dict) else {}\n        hist_peak = parse_float(peak_map.get(code), 0.0)\n        peak_price = max(\n            ref_price,\n            hist_peak,\n            parse_float(prev_state.get(\"peak_price\"), 0.0),\n        )\n        entry_date = entry_dates.get(code, 0)\n        if entry_date <= 0:\n            entry_date = parse_date_tag(prev_state.get(\"entry_date\"))\n        return_pct = pct_change(cost_price, ref_price)\n        peak_return_pct = pct_change(cost_price, peak_price)\n        drawdown_from_peak_pct = pct_change(peak_price, ref_price)\n        armed = bool(prev_state.get(\"armed\", False)) or peak_return_pct >= arm_pct\n        arm_date = prev_state.get(\"arm_date\", \"\")\n        if armed and not arm_date:\n            arm_date = trade_date\n        trailing_triggered = armed and peak_return_pct >= arm_pct and drawdown_from_peak_pct <= -trailing_dd_pct\n        prev_trailing_bars = max(0, parse_int(prev_state.get(\"trailing_trigger_bars\"), 0))\n        prev_trailing_last_date = str(prev_state.get(\"trailing_trigger_last_date\", \"\") or \"\")\n        prev_trailing_start_date = str(prev_state.get(\"trailing_trigger_start_date\", \"\") or \"\")\n        if trailing_triggered:\n            if prev_trailing_bars > 0 and prev_trailing_last_date == trade_date:\n                trailing_trigger_bars = prev_trailing_bars\n                trailing_trigger_start_date = prev_trailing_start_date or trade_date\n            elif prev_trailing_bars > 0:\n                trailing_trigger_bars = prev_trailing_bars + 1\n                trailing_trigger_start_date = prev_trailing_start_date or trade_date\n            else:\n                trailing_trigger_bars = 1\n                trailing_trigger_start_date = trade_date\n            trailing_trigger_last_date = trade_date\n        else:\n            trailing_trigger_bars = 0\n            trailing_trigger_start_date = \"\"\n            trailing_trigger_last_date = \"\"\n        trailing_ma_value = parse_float(trailing_ma_map.get(code), 0.0)\n        stop_loss_stage = str(prev_state.get(\"stop_loss_stage\", \"\") or \"\").strip().lower()\n        if stop_loss_stage not in {\"soft\", \"hard\"}:\n            stop_loss_stage = \"\"\n        if stop_loss_stage == \"soft\":\n            soft_trigger_qty = parse_int(prev_state.get(\"soft_trigger_qty\"), 0)\n            if soft_trigger_qty > 0 and qty > soft_trigger_qty:\n                stop_loss_stage = \"\"\n\n        current_positions[code] = {\n            \"peak_price\": round(peak_price, 6),\n            \"peak_date\": str(latest_trade_date or parse_date_tag(trade_date) or \"\"),\n            \"entry_date\": str(entry_date or \"\"),\n            \"armed\": armed,\n            \"arm_date\": arm_date,\n            \"stop_loss_stage\": stop_loss_stage,\n            \"trailing_trigger_bars\": trailing_trigger_bars,\n            \"trailing_trigger_start_date\": trailing_trigger_start_date,\n            \"trailing_trigger_last_date\": trailing_trigger_last_date,\n            \"trailing_ma_value\": round(trailing_ma_value, 6) if trailing_ma_value > 0 else None,\n            \"last_ref_price\": round(ref_price, 6),\n            \"updated_at\": datetime.now().astimezone().isoformat(),\n        }\n\n        market_value = round(qty * ref_price, 2) if qty > 0 and ref_price > 0 else 0.0\n        record = {\n            \"ts_code\": code,\n            \"qty\": qty,\n            \"cost_price\": cost_price,\n            \"ref_price\": ref_price,\n            \"return_pct\": return_pct,\n            \"peak_price\": peak_price,\n            \"peak_return_pct\": peak_return_pct,\n            \"drawdown_from_peak_pct\": drawdown_from_peak_pct,\n            \"market_value\": market_value,\n            \"in_candidates\": code in candidate_codes,\n            \"buy_score\": parse_float(buy_score_map.get(code), 0.0),\n        }\n        reduce_score, reduce_rank_reason = compute_mode_de_risk_reduce_score(\n            in_candidates=bool(record[\"in_candidates\"]),\n            return_pct=parse_float(record[\"return_pct\"], 0.0),\n            buy_score=parse_float(record[\"buy_score\"], 0.0),\n        )\n        record[\"reduce_score\"] = reduce_score\n        record[\"reduce_rank_reason\"] = reduce_rank_reason\n        holdings_records.append(record)\n\n        if qty <= 0 or ref_price <= 0 or cost_price <= 0:\n            continue\n        if stop_loss_rules.get(\"mode\") == \"dual\":\n            hard_stop_loss_pct = parse_float(stop_loss_rules.get(\"hard_pct\"), -8.0)\n            soft_stop_loss_pct = parse_float(stop_loss_rules.get(\"soft_pct\"), -5.0)\n            soft_sell_ratio = parse_float(stop_loss_rules.get(\"soft_sell_ratio\"), 0.5)\n            if return_pct <= hard_stop_loss_pct:\n                current_positions[code][\"stop_loss_stage\"] = \"hard\"\n                planned_rows.append(\n                    build_exit_signal_row(\n                        trade_date=trade_date,\n                        ts_code=code,\n                        qty=qty,\n                        ref_price=ref_price,\n                        reason=f\"exit_engine:stop_loss_hard 持仓收益={return_pct:.2f}% <= {hard_stop_loss_pct:.2f}%\",\n                        exit_type=\"stop_loss_hard\",\n                        score=1.0,\n                    )\n                )\n                summary[\"stop_loss_count\"] += 1\n                summary[\"stop_loss_hard_count\"] += 1\n                continue\n            if return_pct <= soft_stop_loss_pct:\n                reduce_qty = compute_partial_exit_qty(qty, soft_sell_ratio)\n                if stop_loss_stage == \"soft\":\n                    reduce_qty = resolve_soft_stop_reissue_qty(prev_state, qty, reduce_qty)\n                if reduce_qty >= qty:\n                    current_positions[code][\"stop_loss_stage\"] = \"hard\"\n                    planned_rows.append(\n                        build_exit_signal_row(\n                            trade_date=trade_date,\n                            ts_code=code,\n                            qty=qty,\n                            ref_price=ref_price,\n                            reason=f\"exit_engine:stop_loss_hard 持仓收益={return_pct:.2f}% <= {soft_stop_loss_pct:.2f}% (软止损比例触发全卖)\",\n                            exit_type=\"stop_loss_hard\",\n                            score=1.0,\n                        )\n                    )\n                    summary[\"stop_loss_count\"] += 1\n                    summary[\"stop_loss_hard_count\"] += 1\n                elif reduce_qty > 0:\n                    current_positions[code][\"stop_loss_stage\"] = \"soft\"\n                    current_positions[code][\"stop_loss_soft_trade_date\"] = trade_date\n                    current_positions[code][\"soft_trigger_qty\"] = qty\n                    current_positions[code][\"soft_reduce_qty\"] = reduce_qty\n                    current_positions[code][\"soft_expected_remaining_qty\"] = max(0, qty - reduce_qty)\n                    planned_rows.append(\n                        build_exit_signal_row(\n                            trade_date=trade_date,\n                            ts_code=code,\n                            qty=reduce_qty,\n                            ref_price=ref_price,\n                            reason=(\n                                f\"exit_engine:stop_loss_reduce 持仓收益={return_pct:.2f}% <= {soft_stop_loss_pct:.2f}% \"\n                                f\"减仓比例={soft_sell_ratio * 100:.0f}%\"\n                            ),\n                            exit_type=\"stop_loss_reduce\",\n                            score=0.98,\n                        )\n                    )\n                    summary[\"stop_loss_count\"] += 1\n                    summary[\"stop_loss_reduce_count\"] += 1\n                continue\n        else:\n            stop_loss_pct = parse_float(stop_loss_rules.get(\"single_pct\"), -5.0)\n            if return_pct <= stop_loss_pct:\n                current_positions[code][\"stop_loss_stage\"] = \"hard\"\n                planned_rows.append(\n                    build_exit_signal_row(\n                        trade_date=trade_date,\n                        ts_code=code,\n                        qty=qty,\n                        ref_price=ref_price,\n                        reason=f\"exit_engine:stop_loss 持仓收益={return_pct:.2f}% <= {stop_loss_pct:.2f}%\",\n                        exit_type=\"stop_loss\",\n                        score=1.0,\n                    )\n                )\n                summary[\"stop_loss_count\"] += 1\n                summary[\"stop_loss_hard_count\"] += 1\n                continue\n        trailing_time_confirmed = trailing_trigger_bars >= trailing_confirm_bars\n        trailing_ma_confirmed = (\n            trailing_below_ma_window <= 0\n            or trailing_ma_value <= 0\n            or ref_price <= trailing_ma_value\n        )\n        if trailing_triggered and trailing_time_confirmed and trailing_ma_confirmed:\n            planned_rows.append(\n                build_exit_signal_row(\n                    trade_date=trade_date,\n                    ts_code=code,\n                    qty=qty,\n                    ref_price=ref_price,\n                    reason=(\n                        \"exit_engine:trailing_take_profit \"\n                        f\"峰值收益={peak_return_pct:.2f}% 当前收益={return_pct:.2f}% \"\n                        f\"峰值回撤={drawdown_from_peak_pct:.2f}% \"\n                        f\"confirm_bars={trailing_trigger_bars}/{trailing_confirm_bars}\"\n                        + (\n                            f\" ma{trailing_below_ma_window}={trailing_ma_value:.2f}\"\n                            if trailing_below_ma_window > 0 and trailing_ma_value > 0\n                            else \"\"\n                        )\n                    ),\n                    exit_type=\"trailing_take_profit\",\n                    score=0.95,\n                )\n            )\n            summary[\"trailing_stop_count\"] += 1\n\n    state[\"positions\"] = current_positions\n    save_peak_state(state_path, state)\n\n    total_market_value = sum(parse_float(row[\"market_value\"], 0.0) for row in holdings_records)\n    summary[\"current_exposure\"] = round(total_market_value / account_nav, 4) if account_nav > 0 else None\n\n    planned_sell_codes = {str(row[\"ts_code\"]) for row in planned_rows}\n    planned_sell_value = sum(\n        parse_float(row.get(\"ref_price\"), 0.0) * parse_int(row.get(\"target_qty\"), 0)\n        for row in planned_rows\n    )\n    target_exposure = exposure_target_map.get(mode, 1.0)\n    summary[\"target_exposure\"] = round(target_exposure, 4)\n    residual_market_value = max(0.0, total_market_value - planned_sell_value)\n    summary[\"post_exit_exposure\"] = round(residual_market_value / account_nav, 4) if account_nav > 0 else None\n\n    if mode in {\"cautious\", \"halt\"} and account_nav > 0:\n        target_market_value = account_nav * target_exposure\n        excess_market_value = residual_market_value - target_market_value\n        if excess_market_value > 0:\n            ranked_holdings = sorted(\n                [row for row in holdings_records if row[\"ts_code\"] not in planned_sell_codes],\n                key=lambda row: (\n                    -parse_float(row.get(\"reduce_score\"), 0.0),\n                    row[\"ts_code\"],\n                ),\n            )\n            summary[\"de_risk_ranked_preview\"] = [\n                {\n                    \"ts_code\": str(row[\"ts_code\"]),\n                    \"reduce_score\": round(parse_float(row.get(\"reduce_score\"), 0.0), 6),\n                    \"reduce_rank_reason\": str(row.get(\"reduce_rank_reason\") or \"\"),\n                }\n                for row in ranked_holdings[:5]\n            ]\n            for row in ranked_holdings:\n                if excess_market_value <= 0:\n                    break\n                qty = parse_int(row[\"qty\"], 0)\n                ref_price = parse_float(row[\"ref_price\"], 0.0)\n                if qty <= 0 or ref_price <= 0:\n                    continue\n                if lot_size > 0 and qty > lot_size:\n                    needed_lots = math.ceil(excess_market_value / ref_price / lot_size)\n                    sell_qty = min(qty, max(lot_size, needed_lots * lot_size))\n                else:\n                    sell_qty = qty\n                if sell_qty <= 0:\n                    continue\n                sell_value = min(parse_float(row[\"market_value\"], 0.0), sell_qty * ref_price)\n                excess_market_value -= sell_value\n                planned_rows.append(\n                    build_exit_signal_row(\n                        trade_date=trade_date,\n                        ts_code=str(row[\"ts_code\"]),\n                        qty=sell_qty,\n                        ref_price=ref_price,\n                        reason=(\n                            f\"exit_engine:mode_de_risk mode={mode} \"\n                            f\"目标仓位={target_exposure:.2f} 当前持仓收益={row['return_pct']:.2f}% \"\n                            f\"reduce_score={parse_float(row.get('reduce_score'), 0.0):.3f}\"\n                        ),\n                        exit_type=\"mode_de_risk\",\n                        score=0.8,\n                        reduce_score=parse_float(row.get(\"reduce_score\"), 0.0),\n                        reduce_rank_reason=str(row.get(\"reduce_rank_reason\") or \"\"),\n                    )\n                )\n                summary[\"de_risk_count\"] += 1\n            reduced_market_value = max(\n                0.0,\n                total_market_value\n                - sum(\n                    parse_float(row.get(\"ref_price\"), 0.0) * parse_int(row.get(\"target_qty\"), 0)\n                    for row in planned_rows\n                ),\n            )\n            summary[\"post_exit_exposure\"] = round(reduced_market_value / account_nav, 4) if account_nav > 0 else None\n\n    if not planned_rows:\n        summary[\"reason\"] = \"no_exit_trigger\"\n        return empty, summary\n\n    planned = pd.DataFrame(planned_rows)\n    planned = planned.sort_values([\"ts_code\", \"score\"], ascending=[True, False])\n    planned = planned.drop_duplicates(subset=[\"trade_date\", \"ts_code\", \"signal_type\"], keep=\"first\").reset_index(drop=True)\n    summary[\"exit_rows\"] = int(len(planned))\n    return planned, summary"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":62,"aggregated":"from __future__ import annotations\n\nimport json\nimport math\nimport re\nfrom collections import deque\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Any\n\nimport pandas as pd\n\nDEFAULT_PRICE_HISTORY_PATH = Path(\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/data/a_stock_history.csv\")\n\nBUY_SIDES = {\"BUY\", \"B\", \"LONG\", \"买\"}\n\n\ndef normalize_ts_code(value: Any) -> str:\n    text = str(value or \"\").strip().upper()\n    if not text or text == \"NAN\":\n        return \"\"\n    if text.endswith(\".XSHG\"):\n        return f\"{text[:-5]}.SH\"\n    if text.endswith(\".XSHE\"):\n        return f\"{text[:-5]}.SZ\"\n    if text.endswith((\".SH\", \".SZ\", \".BJ\", \".HK\")):\n        return text\n    if text.isdigit() and len(text) == 6:\n        if text.startswith((\"600\", \"601\", \"603\", \"605\", \"688\")):\n            return f\"{text}.SH\"\n        if text.startswith((\"000\", \"001\", \"002\", \"003\", \"300\", \"301\")):\n            return f\"{text}.SZ\"\n    return text\n\n\ndef is_a_share_stock(ts_code: str) -> bool:\n    code = normalize_ts_code(ts_code)\n    if \".\" not in code:\n        return False\n    symbol, market = code.split(\".\", 1)\n    if market == \"SH\":\n        return symbol.startswith((\"600\", \"601\", \"603\", \"605\", \"688\"))\n    if market == \"SZ\":\n        return symbol.startswith((\"000\", \"001\", \"002\", \"003\", \"300\", \"301\"))\n    return False\n\n\ndef parse_float(value: Any, default: float = 0.0) -> float:\n    try:\n        return float(str(value).replace(\",\", \"\").strip())\n    except Exception:\n        return default\n\n\ndef parse_optional_float(value: Any) -> float | None:\n    if value is None:\n        return None\n    text = str(value).replace(\",\", \"\").strip()\n    if not text or text.lower() == \"none\":\n        return None\n    try:\n        return float(text)\n    except Exception:\n        return None\n\n\ndef parse_int(value: Any, default: int = 0) -> int:\n    try:\n        return int(float(str(value).replace(\",\", \"\").strip()))\n    except Exception:\n        return default\n\n\ndef pct_change(base: float, current: float) -> float:\n    if base <= 0 or current <= 0:\n        return 0.0\n    return (current / base - 1.0) * 100.0\n\n\ndef clamp(value: float, lower: float, upper: float) -> float:\n    return max(lower, min(upper, value))\n\n\ndef parse_date_tag(value: Any) -> int:\n    text = str(value or \"\").strip()\n    digits = re.sub(r\"\\D\", \"\", text)\n    if len(digits) >= 8:\n        return parse_int(digits[:8], 0)\n    return 0\n\n\ndef latest_report_file(report_dir: Path, patterns: list[str], cutoff_date: int = 0) -> Path | None:\n    def sort_key(path: Path) -> tuple[int, float, str]:\n        return (parse_date_tag(path.stem), path.stat().st_mtime, path.name)\n\n    files: list[Path] = []\n    for pattern in patterns:\n        files.extend(report_dir.glob(pattern))\n    if not files:\n        return None\n    if cutoff_date > 0:\n        eligible = [path for path in files if parse_date_tag(path.stem) <= 0 or parse_date_tag(path.stem) <= cutoff_date]\n        if not eligible:\n            return None\n        files = eligible\n    return max(files, key=sort_key)\n\n\ndef resolve_path(value: Any, *, base_dir: Path) -> Path | None:\n    text = str(value or \"\").strip()\n    if not text:\n        return None\n    path = Path(text)\n    if not path.is_absolute():\n        path = (base_dir / path).resolve()\n    return path\n\n\ndef first_existing_column(frame: pd.DataFrame, candidates: list[str]) -> str:\n    for candidate in candidates:\n        if candidate in frame.columns:\n            return candidate\n    return \"\"\n\n\ndef load_holdings(path: Path | None) -> pd.DataFrame:\n    columns = [\"ts_code\", \"qty\", \"cost_price\", \"name\"]\n    if path is None or not path.exists():\n        return pd.DataFrame(columns=columns)\n\n    frame = pd.read_csv(path)\n    if frame.empty:\n        return pd.DataFrame(columns=columns)\n\n    code_col = first_existing_column(frame, [\"ts_code\", \"symbol\", \"security\", \"code\"])\n    qty_col = first_existing_column(frame, [\"qty\", \"quantity\", \"shares\", \"position\", \"current_qty\"])\n    cost_col = first_existing_column(frame, [\"cost_price\", \"cost\", \"avg_cost\", \"hold_cost\", \"price_cost\"])\n    name_col = first_existing_column(frame, [\"name\", \"security_name\"])\n    if not code_col or not qty_col:\n        return pd.DataFrame(columns=columns)\n\n    out = pd.DataFrame()\n    out[\"ts_code\"] = frame[code_col].map(normalize_ts_code)\n    out[\"qty\"] = pd.to_numeric(frame[qty_col], errors=\"coerce\").fillna(0).astype(int)\n    out[\"cost_price\"] = (\n        pd.to_numeric(frame[cost_col], errors=\"coerce\").fillna(0.0) if cost_col else 0.0\n    )\n    out[\"name\"] = frame[name_col].fillna(\"\").astype(str) if name_col else \"\"\n    out = out[(out[\"qty\"] > 0) & out[\"ts_code\"].map(is_a_share_stock)].copy()\n    out = out.drop_duplicates(subset=[\"ts_code\"], keep=\"first\").reset_index(drop=True)\n    return out[columns]\n\n\ndef load_latest_buy_dates(path: Path | None, codes: set[str], cutoff_date: int = 0) -> dict[str, int]:\n    if path is None or not path.exists() or not codes:\n        return {}\n\n    frame = pd.read_csv(path)\n    if frame.empty:\n        return {}\n\n    code_col = first_existing_column(frame, [\"ts_code\", \"symbol\", \"security\", \"code\"])\n    side_col = first_existing_column(frame, [\"side\", \"action\", \"direction\"])\n    date_col = first_existing_column(frame, [\"trade_date\", \"date\", \"biz_date\"])\n    if not code_col or not date_col:\n        return {}\n\n    out = pd.DataFrame()\n    out[\"ts_code\"] = frame[code_col].map(normalize_ts_code)\n    out[\"trade_date\"] = frame[date_col].map(parse_date_tag)\n    if side_col:\n        out[\"side\"] = frame[side_col].fillna(\"\").astype(str).str.upper().str.strip()\n        out = out[out[\"side\"].isin(BUY_SIDES)]\n    out = out[(out[\"trade_date\"] > 0) & out[\"ts_code\"].isin(codes)].copy()\n    if cutoff_date > 0:\n        out = out[out[\"trade_date\"] <= cutoff_date].copy()\n    if out.empty:\n        return {}\n    grouped = out.groupby(\"ts_code\", as_index=False)[\"trade_date\"].max()\n    return dict(zip(grouped[\"ts_code\"], grouped[\"trade_date\"]))\n\n\ndef load_price_snapshot(\n    price_history_path: Path,\n    codes: set[str],\n    entry_dates: dict[str, int],\n    cutoff_date: int = 0,\n) -> tuple[dict[str, float], dict[str, float], int]:\n    latest_close: dict[str, tuple[int, float]] = {}\n    peak_high: dict[str, float] = {code: 0.0 for code in codes}\n    latest_trade_date = 0\n    if not price_history_path.exists() or not codes:\n        return {}, peak_high, latest_trade_date\n\n    for chunk in pd.read_csv(\n        price_history_path,\n        usecols=[\"ts_code\", \"trade_date\", \"high\", \"close\"],\n        chunksize=200000,\n    ):\n        chunk[\"ts_code\"] = chunk[\"ts_code\"].astype(str).str.upper().str.strip()\n        chunk = chunk[chunk[\"ts_code\"].isin(codes)].copy()\n        if chunk.empty:\n            continue\n\n        chunk[\"trade_date\"] = pd.to_numeric(chunk[\"trade_date\"], errors=\"coerce\").fillna(0).astype(int)\n        chunk[\"high\"] = pd.to_numeric(chunk[\"high\"], errors=\"coerce\")\n        chunk[\"close\"] = pd.to_numeric(chunk[\"close\"], errors=\"coerce\")\n        chunk = chunk.dropna(subset=[\"close\"])\n        chunk = chunk[chunk[\"trade_date\"] > 0]\n        if cutoff_date > 0:\n            chunk = chunk[chunk[\"trade_date\"] <= cutoff_date]\n        if chunk.empty:\n            continue\n\n        chunk = chunk.sort_values([\"ts_code\", \"trade_date\"])\n        for row in chunk.itertuples(index=False):\n            code = str(row.ts_code)\n            trade_date = int(row.trade_date)\n            close = parse_float(row.close, 0.0)\n            high = parse_float(row.high, close)\n            latest_trade_date = max(latest_trade_date, trade_date)\n            current = latest_close.get(code)\n            if current is None or trade_date >= current[0]:\n                latest_close[code] = (trade_date, close)\n            entry_date = entry_dates.get(code, 0)\n            if entry_date <= 0 or trade_date >= entry_date:\n                peak_high[code] = max(parse_float(peak_high.get(code), 0.0), high, close)\n\n    close_map = {code: value[1] for code, value in latest_close.items()}\n    return close_map, peak_high, latest_trade_date\n\n\ndef load_latest_ma_snapshot(\n    price_history_path: Path,\n    codes: set[str],\n    window: int,\n    cutoff_date: int = 0,\n) -> dict[str, float]:\n    if not price_history_path.exists() or not codes or window <= 0:\n        return {}\n\n    close_windows: dict[str, deque[float]] = {\n        code: deque(maxlen=max(1, int(window)))\n        for code in codes\n    }\n    for chunk in pd.read_csv(\n        price_history_path,\n        usecols=[\"ts_code\", \"trade_date\", \"close\"],\n        chunksize=200000,\n    ):\n        chunk[\"ts_code\"] = chunk[\"ts_code\"].astype(str).str.upper().str.strip()\n        chunk = chunk[chunk[\"ts_code\"].isin(codes)].copy()\n        if chunk.empty:\n            continue\n\n        chunk[\"trade_date\"] = pd.to_numeric(chunk[\"trade_date\"], errors=\"coerce\").fillna(0).astype(int)\n        chunk[\"close\"] = pd.to_numeric(chunk[\"close\"], errors=\"coerce\")\n        chunk = chunk.dropna(subset=[\"close\"])\n        chunk = chunk[chunk[\"trade_date\"] > 0]\n        if cutoff_date > 0:\n            chunk = chunk[chunk[\"trade_date\"] <= cutoff_date]\n        if chunk.empty:\n            continue\n\n        chunk = chunk.sort_values([\"ts_code\", \"trade_date\"])\n        for row in chunk.itertuples(index=False):\n            code = str(row.ts_code)\n            close = parse_float(row.close, 0.0)\n            if close > 0:\n                close_windows.setdefault(code, deque(maxlen=max(1, int(window)))).append(close)\n\n    ma_map: dict[str, float] = {}\n    for code, values in close_windows.items():\n        if values:\n            ma_map[code] = sum(values) / len(values)\n    return ma_map\n\n\ndef load_peak_state(path: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    if not path.exists():\n        return {\"positions\": {}}\n    try:\n        payload = json.loads(path.read_text(encoding=\"utf-8\"))\n    except Exception:\n        return {\"positions\": {}}\n    if not isinstance(payload, dict):\n        return {\"positions\": {}}\n    positions = payload.get(\"positions\")\n    if not isinstance(positions, dict):\n        payload[\"positions\"] = {}\n    return payload\n\n\ndef save_peak_state(path: Path, state: dict[str, Any]) -> None:\n    path.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    path.write_text(json.dumps(state, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n\n\ndef resolve_exit_config(live_config: dict[str, Any], *, project_root: Path) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    if not isinstance(live_config, dict):\n        live_config = {}\n    defaults: dict[str, Any] = {\n        \"enabled\": True,\n        \"stop_loss_pct\": -5.0,\n        \"stop_loss_soft_pct\": None,\n        \"stop_loss_soft_sell_ratio\": 0.5,\n        \"stop_loss_hard_pct\": None,\n        \"trailing_take_profit_arm_pct\": 8.0,\n        \"trailing_take_profit_drawdown_pct\": 4.0,\n        \"trailing_take_profit_confirm_bars\": 1,\n        \"trailing_take_profit_below_ma_window\": 0,\n        \"mode_cautious_target_exposure\": 0.65,\n        \"mode_halt_target_exposure\": 0.30,\n        \"peak_price_state_path\": \"research/reports/live_exit_peak_state_v1.json\",\n        \"price_history_path\": str(DEFAULT_PRICE_HISTORY_PATH),\n    }\n    block = live_config.get(\"exit_rules\", {}) or {}\n    if isinstance(block, dict):\n        defaults.update({k: v for k, v in block.items() if v not in (None, \"\")})\n    defaults[\"enabled\"] = bool(defaults.get(\"enabled\", True))\n    defaults[\"stop_loss_pct\"] = parse_float(defaults.get(\"stop_loss_pct\"), -5.0)\n    defaults[\"stop_loss_soft_pct\"] = parse_optional_float(defaults.get(\"stop_loss_soft_pct\"))\n    defaults[\"stop_loss_soft_sell_ratio\"] = max(0.0, min(1.0, parse_float(defaults.get(\"stop_loss_soft_sell_ratio\"), 0.5)))\n    defaults[\"stop_loss_hard_pct\"] = parse_optional_float(defaults.get(\"stop_loss_hard_pct\"))\n    for key in [\n        \"trailing_take_profit_arm_pct\",\n        \"trailing_take_profit_drawdown_pct\",\n        \"mode_cautious_target_exposure\",\n        \"mode_halt_target_exposure\",\n    ]:\n        defaults[key] = parse_float(defaults.get(key), parse_float(defaults.get(key), 0.0))\n    defaults[\"trailing_take_profit_confirm_bars\"] = max(\n        1,\n        parse_int(defaults.get(\"trailing_take_profit_confirm_bars\"), 1),\n    )\n    defaults[\"trailing_take_profit_below_ma_window\"] = max(\n        0,\n        parse_int(defaults.get(\"trailing_take_profit_below_ma_window\"), 0),\n    )\n    defaults[\"peak_price_state_path\"] = str(\n        resolve_path(defaults.get(\"peak_price_state_path\"), base_dir=project_root) or \"\"\n    )\n    defaults[\"price_history_path\"] = str(\n        resolve_path(defaults.get(\"price_history_path\"), base_dir=project_root) or DEFAULT_PRICE_HISTORY_PATH\n    )\n    return defaults\n\n\ndef resolve_stop_loss_rules(cfg: dict[str, Any]) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    legacy_pct = parse_optional_float(cfg.get(\"stop_loss_pct\"))\n    soft_pct = parse_optional_float(cfg.get(\"stop_loss_soft_pct\"))\n    hard_pct = parse_optional_float(cfg.get(\"stop_loss_hard_pct\"))\n    soft_sell_ratio = max(0.0, min(1.0, parse_float(cfg.get(\"stop_loss_soft_sell_ratio\"), 0.5)))\n\n    if soft_pct is None and hard_pct is None:\n        return {\n            \"mode\": \"single\",\n            \"single_pct\": legacy_pct if legacy_pct is not None else -5.0,\n            \"soft_pct\": None,\n            \"hard_pct\": None,\n            \"soft_sell_ratio\": 1.0,\n        }\n\n    if soft_pct is None and hard_pct is not None:\n        return {\n            \"mode\": \"single\",\n            \"single_pct\": hard_pct,\n            \"soft_pct\": None,\n            \"hard_pct\": None,\n            \"soft_sell_ratio\": 1.0,\n        }\n\n    if soft_pct is not None and hard_pct is None:\n        hard_pct = legacy_pct if legacy_pct is not None else soft_pct\n\n    ordered = sorted([x for x in [soft_pct, hard_pct] if x is not None], reverse=True)\n    if len(ordered) < 2:\n        return {\n            \"mode\": \"single\",\n            \"single_pct\": ordered[0] if ordered else (legacy_pct if legacy_pct is not None else -5.0),\n            \"soft_pct\": None,\n            \"hard_pct\": None,\n            \"soft_sell_ratio\": 1.0,\n        }\n\n    resolved_soft_pct = ordered[0]\n    resolved_hard_pct = ordered[1]\n    if soft_sell_ratio <= 0.0:\n        return {\n            \"mode\": \"single\",\n            \"single_pct\": resolved_hard_pct,\n            \"soft_pct\": None,\n            \"hard_pct\": None,\n            \"soft_sell_ratio\": 1.0,\n        }\n    if soft_sell_ratio >= 1.0 or resolved_soft_pct <= resolved_hard_pct:\n        return {\n            \"mode\": \"single\",\n            \"single_pct\": resolved_soft_pct,\n            \"soft_pct\": None,\n            \"hard_pct\": None,\n            \"soft_sell_ratio\": 1.0,\n        }\n\n    return {\n        \"mode\": \"dual\",\n        \"single_pct\": None,\n        \"soft_pct\": resolved_soft_pct,\n        \"hard_pct\": resolved_hard_pct,\n        \"soft_sell_ratio\": soft_sell_ratio,\n    }\n\n\ndef compute_partial_exit_qty(qty: int, sell_ratio: float) -> int:\n    if qty <= 0 or sell_ratio <= 0:\n        return 0\n    return min(qty, max(1, int(math.ceil(qty * sell_ratio))))\n\n\ndef resolve_soft_stop_reissue_qty(prev_state: dict[str, Any], current_qty: int, default_reduce_qty: int) -> int:\n    trigger_qty = parse_int(prev_state.get(\"soft_trigger_qty\"), 0)\n    remaining_qty = parse_int(prev_state.get(\"soft_expected_remaining_qty\"), -1)\n    reduce_qty = parse_int(prev_state.get(\"soft_reduce_qty\"), 0)\n\n    if trigger_qty > 0 and current_qty > trigger_qty:\n        return default_reduce_qty\n\n    if remaining_qty < 0:\n        return 0\n    if current_qty <= remaining_qty:\n        return 0\n\n    pending_reduce_qty = current_qty - remaining_qty\n    if reduce_qty > 0:\n        pending_reduce_qty = min(pending_reduce_qty, reduce_qty)\n    return max(0, pending_reduce_qty)\n\n\ndef build_exit_signal_row(\n    *,\n    trade_date: str,\n    ts_code: str,\n    qty: int,\n    ref_price: float,\n    reason: str,\n    exit_type: str,\n    score: float,\n    reduce_score: float | None = None,\n    reduce_rank_reason: str = \"\",\n) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    now_text = datetime.now().astimezone().isoformat()\n    return {\n        \"trade_date\": trade_date,\n        \"ts_code\": ts_code,\n        \"signal_type\": \"SELL\",\n        \"score\": round(score, 6),\n        \"target_weight\": 0.0,\n        \"target_qty\": int(max(0, qty)),\n        \"ref_price\": round(ref_price, 4) if ref_price > 0 else None,\n        \"strategy_id\": \"exit_engine_v1\",\n        \"risk_flag\": \"exit_engine\",\n        \"comment\": reason,\n        \"source_run_id\": f\"exit_engine_v1_{trade_date.replace('-', '')}\",\n        \"generated_at\": now_text,\n        \"approved\": True,\n        \"risk_status\": \"exit\",\n        \"risk_adjustment\": exit_type,\n        \"exit_type\": exit_type,\n        \"exit_reason\": reason,\n        \"reason\": reason,\n        \"reduce_score\": round(parse_float(reduce_score, 0.0), 6) if reduce_score is not None else None,\n        \"reduce_rank_reason\": reduce_rank_reason,\n    }\n\n\ndef compute_mode_de_risk_reduce_score(\n    *,\n    in_candidates: bool,\n    return_pct: float,\n    buy_score: float,\n) -> tuple[float, str]:\n    non_candidate_bonus = 10.0 if not in_candidates else 0.0\n    return_component = clamp(-parse_float(return_pct, 0.0) / 5.0, -2.0, 2.0)\n    weak_buy_component = 0.5 * (1.0 - clamp(parse_float(buy_score, 0.0), 0.0, 1.0))\n    total = non_candidate_bonus + return_component + weak_buy_component\n    detail = (\n        f\"non_candidate_bonus={non_candidate_bonus:.2f};\"\n        f\"return_component={return_component:.2f};\"\n        f\"weak_buy_component={weak_buy_component:.2f}\"\n    )\n    return round(total, 6), detail\n\n\ndef generate_exit_signals(\n    *,\n    trade_date: str,\n    account_nav: float,\n    mode: str,\n    live_config: dict[str, Any],\n    project_root: Path,\n    report_dir: Path,\n    holdings_path: Path | None,\n    trade_history_path: Path | None = None,\n    lot_size: int = 100,\n    candidate_codes: set[str] | None = None,\n    buy_score_map: dict[str, float] | None = None,\n) -> tuple[pd.DataFrame, dict[str, Any]]:\n    cfg = resolve_exit_config(live_config, project_root=project_root)\n    summary: dict[str, Any] = {\n        \"enabled\": bool(cfg.get(\"enabled\", True)),\n        \"holdings_path\": \"\",\n        \"trade_history_path\": \"\",\n        \"holdings_count\": 0,\n        \"price_hit_count\": 0,\n        \"stop_loss_count\": 0,\n        \"stop_loss_reduce_count\": 0,\n        \"stop_loss_hard_count\": 0,\n        \"trailing_stop_count\": 0,\n        \"de_risk_count\": 0,\n        \"mode\": mode,\n        \"target_exposure\": None,\n        \"current_exposure\": None,\n        \"post_exit_exposure\": None,\n        \"state_path\": str(cfg.get(\"peak_price_state_path\", \"\")),\n        \"de_risk_score_rule\": (\n            \"reduce_score=10*(非候选股) + clip(-return_pct/5,-2,2) + 0.5*(1-clamp(buy_score,0,1))\"\n        ),\n    }\n    empty = pd.DataFrame()\n    if not bool(cfg.get(\"enabled\", True)):\n        summary[\"reason\"] = \"disabled\"\n        return empty, summary\n    cutoff_date = parse_date_tag(trade_date)\n\n    holdings_file = holdings_path\n    if holdings_file is None:\n        holdings_file = latest_report_file(\n            report_dir,\n            [\"broker_api_holdings_*.csv\", \"ths_app_holdings_*.csv\", \"account_holdings_*.csv\"],\n            cutoff_date=cutoff_date,\n        )\n    if holdings_file is None or not holdings_file.exists():\n        summary[\"reason\"] = \"holdings_not_found\"\n        return empty, summary\n    summary[\"holdings_path\"] = str(holdings_file)\n\n    holdings = load_holdings(holdings_file)\n    summary[\"holdings_count\"] = int(len(holdings))\n    if holdings.empty:\n        summary[\"reason\"] = \"holdings_empty\"\n        return empty, summary\n\n    if trade_history_path is None:\n        trade_history_path = latest_report_file(\n            report_dir,\n            [\"ths_app_trades_*.csv\", \"ths_trades_*.csv\"],\n            cutoff_date=cutoff_date,\n        )\n    if trade_history_path is not None and trade_history_path.exists():\n        summary[\"trade_history_path\"] = str(trade_history_path)\n\n    codes = set(holdings[\"ts_code\"].tolist())\n    entry_dates = load_latest_buy_dates(trade_history_path, codes, cutoff_date=cutoff_date)\n\n    state_path = Path(str(cfg[\"peak_price_state_path\"]))\n    state = load_peak_state(state_path)\n    old_positions = state.get(\"positions\", {}) or {}\n    for code, payload in old_positions.items():\n        if code not in entry_dates and isinstance(payload, dict):\n            entry_date = parse_date_tag(payload.get(\"entry_date\"))\n            if entry_date > 0:\n                entry_dates[code] = entry_date\n\n    close_map, peak_map, latest_trade_date = load_price_snapshot(\n        Path(str(cfg[\"price_history_path\"])),\n        codes,\n        entry_dates,\n        cutoff_date=cutoff_date,\n    )\n    summary[\"price_hit_count\"] = int(sum(1 for code in codes if parse_float(close_map.get(code), 0.0) > 0))\n\n    candidate_codes = {normalize_ts_code(code) for code in (candidate_codes or set()) if normalize_ts_code(code)}\n    buy_score_map = {normalize_ts_code(k): parse_float(v, 0.0) for k, v in (buy_score_map or {}).items()}\n    stop_loss_rules = resolve_stop_loss_rules(cfg)\n    summary[\"stop_loss_mode\"] = str(stop_loss_rules.get(\"mode\", \"single\"))\n    if stop_loss_rules.get(\"mode\") == \"dual\":\n        summary[\"stop_loss_soft_pct\"] = stop_loss_rules.get(\"soft_pct\")\n        summary[\"stop_loss_hard_pct\"] = stop_loss_rules.get(\"hard_pct\")\n        summary[\"stop_loss_soft_sell_ratio\"] = stop_loss_rules.get(\"soft_sell_ratio\")\n    else:\n        summary[\"stop_loss_pct\"] = stop_loss_rules.get(\"single_pct\")\n    arm_pct = parse_float(cfg.get(\"trailing_take_profit_arm_pct\"), 8.0)\n    trailing_dd_pct = abs(parse_float(cfg.get(\"trailing_take_profit_drawdown_pct\"), 4.0))\n    trailing_confirm_bars = max(1, parse_int(cfg.get(\"trailing_take_profit_confirm_bars\"), 1))\n    trailing_below_ma_window = max(0, parse_int(cfg.get(\"trailing_take_profit_below_ma_window\"), 0))\n    summary[\"trailing_take_profit_arm_pct\"] = arm_pct\n    summary[\"trailing_take_profit_drawdown_pct\"] = trailing_dd_pct\n    summary[\"trailing_take_profit_confirm_bars\"] = trailing_confirm_bars\n    summary[\"trailing_take_profit_below_ma_window\"] = trailing_below_ma_window\n    trailing_ma_map = load_latest_ma_snapshot(\n        Path(str(cfg[\"price_history_path\"])),\n        codes,\n        trailing_below_ma_window,\n        cutoff_date=cutoff_date,\n    ) if trailing_below_ma_window > 0 else {}\n    exposure_target_map = {\n        \"normal\": 1.0,\n        \"cautious\": max(0.0, min(1.0, parse_float(cfg.get(\"mode_cautious_target_exposure\"), 0.65))),\n        \"halt\": max(0.0, min(1.0, parse_float(cfg.get(\"mode_halt_target_exposure\"), 0.30))),\n    }\n\n    planned_rows: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n    current_positions: dict[str, dict[str, Any]] = {}\n    holdings_records: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n    for row in holdings.to_dict(orient=\"records\"):\n        code = str(row[\"ts_code\"])\n        qty = parse_int(row.get(\"qty\"), 0)\n        cost_price = parse_float(row.get(\"cost_price\"), 0.0)\n        ref_price = parse_float(close_map.get(code), 0.0)\n        prev_state = old_positions.get(code, {}) if isinstance(old_positions.get(code), dict) else {}\n        hist_peak = parse_float(peak_map.get(code), 0.0)\n        peak_price = max(\n            ref_price,\n            hist_peak,\n            parse_float(prev_state.get(\"peak_price\"), 0.0),\n        )\n        entry_date = entry_dates.get(code, 0)\n        if entry_date <= 0:\n            entry_date = parse_date_tag(prev_state.get(\"entry_date\"))\n        return_pct = pct_change(cost_price, ref_price)\n        peak_return_pct = pct_change(cost_price, peak_price)\n        drawdown_from_peak_pct = pct_change(peak_price, ref_price)\n        armed = bool(prev_state.get(\"armed\", False)) or peak_return_pct >= arm_pct\n        arm_date = prev_state.get(\"arm_date\", \"\")\n        if armed and not arm_date:\n            arm_date = trade_date\n        trailing_triggered = armed and peak_return_pct >= arm_pct and drawdown_from_peak_pct <= -trailing_dd_pct\n        prev_trailing_bars = max(0, parse_int(prev_state.get(\"trailing_trigger_bars\"), 0))\n        prev_trailing_last_date = str(prev_state.get(\"trailing_trigger_last_date\", \"\") or \"\")\n        prev_trailing_start_date = str(prev_state.get(\"trailing_trigger_start_date\", \"\") or \"\")\n        if trailing_triggered:\n            if prev_trailing_bars > 0 and prev_trailing_last_date == trade_date:\n                trailing_trigger_bars = prev_trailing_bars\n                trailing_trigger_start_date = prev_trailing_start_date or trade_date\n            elif prev_trailing_bars > 0:\n                trailing_trigger_bars = prev_trailing_bars + 1\n                trailing_trigger_start_date = prev_trailing_start_date or trade_date\n            else:\n                trailing_trigger_bars = 1\n                trailing_trigger_start_date = trade_date\n            trailing_trigger_last_date = trade_date\n        else:\n            trailing_trigger_bars = 0\n            trailing_trigger_start_date = \"\"\n            trailing_trigger_last_date = \"\"\n        trailing_ma_value = parse_float(trailing_ma_map.get(code), 0.0)\n        stop_loss_stage = str(prev_state.get(\"stop_loss_stage\", \"\") or \"\").strip().lower()\n        if stop_loss_stage not in {\"soft\", \"hard\"}:\n            stop_loss_stage = \"\"\n        if stop_loss_stage == \"soft\":\n            soft_trigger_qty = parse_int(prev_state.get(\"soft_trigger_qty\"), 0)\n            if soft_trigger_qty > 0 and qty > soft_trigger_qty:\n                stop_loss_stage = \"\"\n\n        current_positions[code] = {\n            \"peak_price\": round(peak_price, 6),\n            \"peak_date\": str(latest_trade_date or parse_date_tag(trade_date) or \"\"),\n            \"entry_date\": str(entry_date or \"\"),\n            \"armed\": armed,\n            \"arm_date\": arm_date,\n            \"stop_loss_stage\": stop_loss_stage,\n            \"trailing_trigger_bars\": trailing_trigger_bars,\n            \"trailing_trigger_start_date\": trailing_trigger_start_date,\n            \"trailing_trigger_last_date\": trailing_trigger_last_date,\n            \"trailing_ma_value\": round(trailing_ma_value, 6) if trailing_ma_value > 0 else None,\n            \"last_ref_price\": round(ref_price, 6),\n            \"updated_at\": datetime.now().astimezone().isoformat(),\n        }\n\n        market_value = round(qty * ref_price, 2) if qty > 0 and ref_price > 0 else 0.0\n        record = {\n            \"ts_code\": code,\n            \"qty\": qty,\n            \"cost_price\": cost_price,\n            \"ref_price\": ref_price,\n            \"return_pct\": return_pct,\n            \"peak_price\": peak_price,\n            \"peak_return_pct\": peak_return_pct,\n            \"drawdown_from_peak_pct\": drawdown_from_peak_pct,\n            \"market_value\": market_value,\n            \"in_candidates\": code in candidate_codes,\n            \"buy_score\": parse_float(buy_score_map.get(code), 0.0),\n        }\n        reduce_score, reduce_rank_reason = compute_mode_de_risk_reduce_score(\n            in_candidates=bool(record[\"in_candidates\"]),\n            return_pct=parse_float(record[\"return_pct\"], 0.0),\n            buy_score=parse_float(record[\"buy_score\"], 0.0),\n        )\n        record[\"reduce_score\"] = reduce_score\n        record[\"reduce_rank_reason\"] = reduce_rank_reason\n        holdings_records.append(record)\n\n        if qty <= 0 or ref_price <= 0 or cost_price <= 0:\n            continue\n        if stop_loss_rules.get(\"mode\") == \"dual\":\n            hard_stop_loss_pct = parse_float(stop_loss_rules.get(\"hard_pct\"), -8.0)\n            soft_stop_loss_pct = parse_float(stop_loss_rules.get(\"soft_pct\"), -5.0)\n            soft_sell_ratio = parse_float(stop_loss_rules.get(\"soft_sell_ratio\"), 0.5)\n            if return_pct <= hard_stop_loss_pct:\n                current_positions[code][\"stop_loss_stage\"] = \"hard\"\n                planned_rows.append(\n                    build_exit_signal_row(\n                        trade_date=trade_date,\n                        ts_code=code,\n                        qty=qty,\n                        ref_price=ref_price,\n                        reason=f\"exit_engine:stop_loss_hard 持仓收益={return_pct:.2f}% <= {hard_stop_loss_pct:.2f}%\",\n                        exit_type=\"stop_loss_hard\",\n                        score=1.0,\n                    )\n                )\n                summary[\"stop_loss_count\"] += 1\n                summary[\"stop_loss_hard_count\"] += 1\n                continue\n            if return_pct <= soft_stop_loss_pct:\n                reduce_qty = compute_partial_exit_qty(qty, soft_sell_ratio)\n                if stop_loss_stage == \"soft\":\n                    reduce_qty = resolve_soft_stop_reissue_qty(prev_state, qty, reduce_qty)\n                if reduce_qty >= qty:\n                    current_positions[code][\"stop_loss_stage\"] = \"hard\"\n                    planned_rows.append(\n                        build_exit_signal_row(\n                            trade_date=trade_date,\n                            ts_code=code,\n                            qty=qty,\n                            ref_price=ref_price,\n                            reason=f\"exit_engine:stop_loss_hard 持仓收益={return_pct:.2f}% <= {soft_stop_loss_pct:.2f}% (软止损比例触发全卖)\",\n                            exit_type=\"stop_loss_hard\",\n                            score=1.0,\n                        )\n                    )\n                    summary[\"stop_loss_count\"] += 1\n                    summary[\"stop_loss_hard_count\"] += 1\n                elif reduce_qty > 0:\n                    current_positions[code][\"stop_loss_stage\"] = \"soft\"\n                    current_positions[code][\"stop_loss_soft_trade_date\"] = trade_date\n                    current_positions[code][\"soft_trigger_qty\"] = qty\n                    current_positions[code][\"soft_reduce_qty\"] = reduce_qty\n                    current_positions[code][\"soft_expected_remaining_qty\"] = max(0, qty - reduce_qty)\n                    planned_rows.append(\n                        build_exit_signal_row(\n                            trade_date=trade_date,\n                            ts_code=code,\n                            qty=reduce_qty,\n                            ref_price=ref_price,\n                            reason=(\n                                f\"exit_engine:stop_loss_reduce 持仓收益={return_pct:.2f}% <= {soft_stop_loss_pct:.2f}% \"\n                                f\"减仓比例={soft_sell_ratio * 100:.0f}%\"\n                            ),\n                            exit_type=\"stop_loss_reduce\",\n                            score=0.98,\n                        )\n                    )\n                    summary[\"stop_loss_count\"] += 1\n                    summary[\"stop_loss_reduce_count\"] += 1\n                continue\n        else:\n            stop_loss_pct = parse_float(stop_loss_rules.get(\"single_pct\"), -5.0)\n            if return_pct <= stop_loss_pct:\n                current_positions[code][\"stop_loss_stage\"] = \"hard\"\n                planned_rows.append(\n                    build_exit_signal_row(\n                        trade_date=trade_date,\n                        ts_code=code,\n                        qty=qty,\n                        ref_price=ref_price,\n                        reason=f\"exit_engine:stop_loss 持仓收益={return_pct:.2f}% <= {stop_loss_pct:.2f}%\",\n                        exit_type=\"stop_loss\",\n                        score=1.0,\n                    )\n                )\n                summary[\"stop_loss_count\"] += 1\n                summary[\"stop_loss_hard_count\"] += 1\n                continue\n        trailing_time_confirmed = trailing_trigger_bars >= trailing_confirm_bars\n        trailing_ma_confirmed = (\n            trailing_below_ma_window <= 0\n            or trailing_ma_value <= 0\n            or ref_price <= trailing_ma_value\n        )\n        if trailing_triggered and trailing_time_confirmed and trailing_ma_confirmed:\n            planned_rows.append(\n                build_exit_signal_row(\n                    trade_date=trade_date,\n                    ts_code=code,\n                    qty=qty,\n                    ref_price=ref_price,\n                    reason=(\n                        \"exit_engine:trailing_take_profit \"\n                        f\"峰值收益={peak_return_pct:.2f}% 当前收益={return_pct:.2f}% \"\n                        f\"峰值回撤={drawdown_from_peak_pct:.2f}% \"\n                        f\"confirm_bars={trailing_trigger_bars}/{trailing_confirm_bars}\"\n                        + (\n                            f\" ma{trailing_below_ma_window}={trailing_ma_value:.2f}\"\n                            if trailing_below_ma_window > 0 and trailing_ma_value > 0\n                            else \"\"\n                        )\n                    ),\n                    exit_type=\"trailing_take_profit\",\n                    score=0.95,\n                )\n            )\n            summary[\"trailing_stop_count\"] += 1\n\n    state[\"positions\"] = current_positions\n    save_peak_state(state_path, state)\n\n    total_market_value = sum(parse_float(row[\"market_value\"], 0.0) for row in holdings_records)\n    summary[\"current_exposure\"] = round(total_market_value / account_nav, 4) if account_nav > 0 else None\n\n    planned_sell_codes = {str(row[\"ts_code\"]) for row in planned_rows}\n    planned_sell_value = sum(\n        parse_float(row.get(\"ref_price\"), 0.0) * parse_int(row.get(\"target_qty\"), 0)\n        for row in planned_rows\n    )\n    target_exposure = exposure_target_map.get(mode, 1.0)\n    summary[\"target_exposure\"] = round(target_exposure, 4)\n    residual_market_value = max(0.0, total_market_value - planned_sell_value)\n    summary[\"post_exit_exposure\"] = round(residual_market_value / account_nav, 4) if account_nav > 0 else None\n\n    if mode in {\"cautious\", \"halt\"} and account_nav > 0:\n        target_market_value = account_nav * target_exposure\n        excess_market_value = residual_market_value - target_market_value\n        if excess_market_value > 0:\n            ranked_holdings = sorted(\n                [row for row in holdings_records if row[\"ts_code\"] not in planned_sell_codes],\n                key=lambda row: (\n                    -parse_float(row.get(\"reduce_score\"), 0.0),\n                    row[\"ts_code\"],\n                ),\n            )\n            summary[\"de_risk_ranked_preview\"] = [\n                {\n                    \"ts_code\": str(row[\"ts_code\"]),\n                    \"reduce_score\": round(parse_float(row.get(\"reduce_score\"), 0.0), 6),\n                    \"reduce_rank_reason\": str(row.get(\"reduce_rank_reason\") or \"\"),\n                }\n                for row in ranked_holdings[:5]\n            ]\n            for row in ranked_holdings:\n                if excess_market_value <= 0:\n                    break\n                qty = parse_int(row[\"qty\"], 0)\n                ref_price = parse_float(row[\"ref_price\"], 0.0)\n                if qty <= 0 or ref_price <= 0:\n                    continue\n                if lot_size > 0 and qty > lot_size:\n                    needed_lots = math.ceil(excess_market_value / ref_price / lot_size)\n                    sell_qty = min(qty, max(lot_size, needed_lots * lot_size))\n                else:\n                    sell_qty = qty\n                if sell_qty <= 0:\n                    continue\n                sell_value = min(parse_float(row[\"market_value\"], 0.0), sell_qty * ref_price)\n                excess_market_value -= sell_value\n                planned_rows.append(\n                    build_exit_signal_row(\n                        trade_date=trade_date,\n                        ts_code=str(row[\"ts_code\"]),\n                        qty=sell_qty,\n                        ref_price=ref_price,\n                        reason=(\n                            f\"exit_engine:mode_de_risk mode={mode} \"\n                            f\"目标仓位={target_exposure:.2f} 当前持仓收益={row['return_pct']:.2f}% \"\n                            f\"reduce_score={parse_float(row.get('reduce_score'), 0.0):.3f}\"\n                        ),\n                        exit_type=\"mode_de_risk\",\n                        score=0.8,\n                        reduce_score=parse_float(row.get(\"reduce_score\"), 0.0),\n                        reduce_rank_reason=str(row.get(\"reduce_rank_reason\") or \"\"),\n                    )\n                )\n                summary[\"de_risk_count\"] += 1\n            reduced_market_value = max(\n                0.0,\n                total_market_value\n                - sum(\n                    parse_float(row.get(\"ref_price\"), 0.0) * parse_int(row.get(\"target_qty\"), 0)\n                    for row in planned_rows\n                ),\n            )\n            summary[\"post_exit_exposure\"] = round(reduced_market_value / account_nav, 4) if account_nav > 0 else None\n\n    if not planned_rows:\n        summary[\"reason\"] = \"no_exit_trigger\"\n        return empty, summary\n\n    planned = pd.DataFrame(planned_rows)\n    planned = planned.sort_values([\"ts_code\", \"score\"], ascending=[True, False])\n    planned = planned.drop_duplicates(subset=[\"trade_date\", \"ts_code\", \"signal_type\"], keep=\"first\").reset_index(drop=True)\n    summary[\"exit_rows\"] = int(len(planned))\n    return planned, summary","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774843834478}}
{"type":"message","id":"df6d4492","parentId":"d9cd5096","timestamp":"2026-03-30T04:10:54.550Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a comprehensive exit engine. Let me summarize the key strategies clearly for Zhang Ling.","thinkingSignature":"24d1c361ea322ba8ebc16e2b389b3755ad749c367c5571da7712ddd83883081a"},{"type":"text","text":"止盈（追踪止盈）策略的核心逻辑：\n\n---\n\n## 追踪止盈（Trailing Take-Profit）\n\n**触发条件（三重门，需要同时满足）：**\n\n1. **Arm 已激活**：持仓从成本价起算的峰值收益 ≥ `arm_pct`（默认 **8%**）\n   - 一旦触发，以后每天都算\"已武装\"状态，不再需要重新满足峰值收益条件\n\n2. **从峰值回撤 ≥ `drawdown_pct`（默认 4%）**\n   - 即：从账户曾经达到的最高价，往下亏了 4% 以上就触发\n\n3. **时间确认**：连续 `confirm_bars`（默认 1 天）都满足条件\n\n**可选附加条件：MA 过滤**\n- 如果配置了 `trailing_take_profit_below_ma_window`（默认 0，即不启用）\n- 当前价必须跌到 MA 均线下方才触发\n\n**举例说明：**\n```\n成本价：10元\n涨到 10.8元（峰值，收益 8%）→ Arm 激活，记录峰值 10.8 元\n回调到 10.4 元（回撤 3.7%）：不触发\n回调到 10.37 元（回撤 4%，刚好达到 4%）→ 触发止盈\n```\n\n---\n\n## 止损策略（Stop-Loss，两档模式）\n\n**Soft（软止损）**：\n- 收益 ≤ `soft_pct`（默认 -5%）→ 卖出 50% 仓位（`soft_sell_ratio`）\n- 剩余 50% 继续持有，等待硬止损\n\n**Hard（硬止损）**：\n- 收益 ≤ `hard_pct`（默认 -8%）→ 全部清仓\n\n---\n\n## 组合风控降仓（Mode De-Risk）\n\n当策略进入 `cautious` 或 `halt` 模式时，还会根据组合目标仓位缺口，**对未触发止盈/止损的持仓主动排序减仓**：\n\n- 排序分数 = 10×非候选股加成 + 收益负贡献 + 弱信号加成\n- 优先卖出不在候选列表里、持仓亏损、信号弱的股票\n\n---\n\n## 为什么 aggressive 纸纸账户 20260320 全清？\n\naggressive 的 exit config 启用了 `trailing_take_profit`（8% 激活 + 4% 回撤），同时处于 `halt` 模式（目标仓位 30%）。\n\n20260320 当天，三只持仓的峰值收益都达到了 8% 的 Arm 线，但随后触发 4% 回撤的止盈信号，且 `halt` 模式要求压低到 30% 仓位，三重退出叠加 → 全部清仓。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":28379,"output":594,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53993,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774843834494,"responseId":"06192abacda1a7d6ce02dae0f368b42a"}}
