er_indicator.trade_value` 统计。\n- 扫描结果：grid=108，达成收益回撤约束 74 组，但 `turnover_ratio<=0.65` 为 0 组。\n- 当前低换手优先候选：topk=12, n_drop=1, hold=5, risk=0.4，年化 48.94%，回撤 23.17%，夏普 2.641，turnover_ratio 62.7998。\n\n## 07:18 执行遗漏感知问题复盘（Durable）\n- 用户指出“忘记执行任务”，根因是对“先对齐再执行”机械化处理，在“继续任务/看报告”场景先反问，造成延迟感知。\n- 已修正流程：收到“继续任务/我要看报告/先给结果”时，优先直接汇报当前进度+报告路径，再进入下一步执行。\n- 已落地文件：`AGENTS.md`、`USER.md`、`.learnings/LEARNINGS.md`。\n\n## 07:22 纸面实盘最终候选清单（Durable）\n- 用户确认“好的”后，已直接产出最终候选与仓位建议（不再二次确认阻塞）。\n- 新增报告：`quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper\n\nSource: memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-07.full.md#L1-L32","source":"memory","citation":"memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-07.full.md#L1-L32"},{"path":"memory/nightly_distill/2026-03-28.md","startLine":1,"endLine":36,"score":0.3828522831201553,"snippet":"# 夜跑提炼 2026-03-28\n\n- started_at: 2026-03-28 23:02:50\n- source_memory: `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-28.md`\n- source_learnings: `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/.learnings/LEARNINGS.md`\n- source_nonempty_lines: 91\n\n## 高频主题\n- 量化: 4\n- 飞书: 2\n- 面板: 0\n- 模拟盘: 0\n- 规则: 0\n- 自动: 0\n- 中文: 0\n- 持仓: 5\n- 报告: 1\n- 夜跑: 0\n\n## 今日提炼\n- 用户明确要求：当前飞书账号 `feishu-assistant` 应关联到 agent `xiaoguanjia`，而不是 `main`。\n- 已将 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` 中 `accountId=feishu-assistant` 的绑定改为 `agentId=xiaoguanjia`；`channels.feishu.defaultAccount` 暂未改动，因为它是全局默认出站账号，贸然修改会扩大影响面。\n- Source: memory-lancedb-pro/self_improvement_log\n- Source: memory-lancedb-pro/self_improvement_log\n- Source: memory-lancedb-pro/self_improveme\n\nSource: memory/nightly_distill/2026-03-28.md#L1-L36","source":"memory","citation":"memory/nightly_distill/2026-03-28.md#L1-L36"},{"path":"memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-08-skill-evaluation.full.md","startLine":466,"endLine":466,"score":0.3755854696035385,"snippet":"\"stderr_tail\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/skills/stock-daily-report/generate_report.py:418: UserWarning: Glyph 27946 (\\\\N{CJK UNIFIED IDEOGRAPH-6D2A}) missing from font(s) DejaVu Sans.\\n plt.savefig(buf, dpi=100, bbox_inches='tight', facecolor='white', format='png')\\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/skills/stock-daily-report/generate_report.py:418: UserWarning: Glyph 27719 (\\\\N{CJK UNIFIED IDEOGRAPH-6C47}) missing from font(s) DejaVu Sans.\\n plt.savefig(buf, dpi=100, bbox_inches='tight', facecolor='white', format='png')\\n/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/skills/stock-daily-report/generate_report.py:418: UserWarning: Glyph 26032 (\\\\N{CJK UNIFIED IDEOGRAPH-65B0}) missing from font(s) DejaV\n\nSource: memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-08-skill-evaluation.full.md#L466","source":"memory","citation":"memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-08-skill-evaluation.full.md#L466"},{"path":"memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-08-skill-evaluation.full.md","startLine":362,"endLine":419,"score":0.3817779093980789,"snippet":"如果你同意，我下一步直接帮你把这个新 skill 接管你现在的 09:25 推送任务（替换旧的 stock-daily-report 定时任务）。\nassistant: 可以，而且我已经给你做完了 ✅\n我新建了一个融合版专业 A 股 skill：**`a-share-fusion-report`**\n\n### 已完成内容\n- 新 skill 路径：\n- `~/.openclaw/skills/a-share-fusion-report`\n- 工作区源码：`/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/skills/a-share-fusion-report`\n- 核心脚本：\n- `scripts/run_fusion_report.py`\n- `scripts/install_cron_0925.sh`\n\n### 这个新 skill 融合了三者优点\n1) **stock-daily-report**：主报告引擎（专业 HTML 报告）\n2) **stock-watcher**：快速行情回退（主引擎失败也能给你可读结果）\n3) **akshare-stock**：资金流专业叠加（主力净流入等）\n\n### 关键能力\n- 自动读取你最新持仓（优先 `ths_web_holding_count_fix_*.json`）\n- 自动同步到两个 watchlist（daily-report + stock-watcher）\n- 生成融合版 `md/json` 报告\n- 可选飞书推送\n- 可选“仅交易日执行”保护\n\n### 实测结果\n我已经试跑成功（proxy 关闭后）：\n-\n\nSource: memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-08-skill-evaluation.full.md#L362-L419","source":"memory","citation":"memory/archive/2026-03/2026-03-08-skill-evaluation.full.md#L362-L419"},{"path":"memory/knowledge/20260305_112245_个人量化投资系统.md","startLine":1,"endLine":10,"score":0.3687510550022125,"snippet":"# 个人量化投资系统\n\n**日期**: 2026-03-05 11:22:45\n**分类**: 知识库\n**标签**: 无\n\n---\n\n正在开发中，使用Tushare获取数据，已下载654万条A股历史数据\n\nSource: memory/knowledge/20260305_11