{"type":"message","id":"14b20010","parentId":"70e6bdf7","timestamp":"2026-03-30T12:53:40.437Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_rqxu64b9v1mm_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"__pycache__\ncron_weibo_monitor.py\nfetch_and_report.py\nkol_uids.json\nlast_fetch.json\nreport_20260323_1628.txt\nreport_20260323_1655.txt"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":38,"aggregated":"__pycache__\ncron_weibo_monitor.py\nfetch_and_report.py\nkol_uids.json\nlast_fetch.json\nreport_20260323_1628.txt\nreport_20260323_1655.txt","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774875220423}}
{"type":"message","id":"63bbcd28","parentId":"14b20010","timestamp":"2026-03-30T12:53:40.453Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_rqxu64b9v1mm_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n微博财经大V监控 - 定时推送脚本\n每天两次：08:30（盘前） 和 20:00（收盘后）\n\"\"\"\nimport json, subprocess, sys\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n# ── 配置 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nWORKSPACE = Path.home() / \".openclaw\" / \"workspace\"\nREPORT_DIR = WORKSPACE / \"weibo_monitor_reports\"\nSTATE_FILE = WORKSPACE / \"weibo_monitor_state.json\"\nCONFIG_FILE = WORKSPACE / \"config\" / \"investment_research_delivery_v1.json\"\n\nFEISHU_TARGET = \"chat:oc_8a819be3a90d35b8d0a2d5c1f4642b22\"  # 来福研讨会群\nOPENCLAW_BIN = str(Path.home() / \".local\" / \"share\" / \"fnm\" / \"aliases\" / \"default\" / \"bin\" / \"openclaw\")\n\nsys.path.insert(0, str(Path(__file__).parent))\nfrom fetch_and_report import fetch_all_kols, build_report, save_state\n\n# ── 工具 ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\ndef send_feishu(message: str, dry_run: bool = False) -> tuple:\n    cmd = [\n        OPENCLAW_BIN,\n        \"message\", \"send\",\n        \"--channel\", \"feishu\",\n        \"--target\", FEISHU_TARGET,\n        \"-m\", message,\n    ]\n    if dry_run:\n        cmd.append(\"--dry-run\")\n    try:\n        result = subprocess.run(cmd, capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=60)\n        return result.returncode == 0, result.stdout[:500] or result.stderr[:500]\n    except Exception as e:\n        return False, str(e)\n\n# ── 主程序 ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\ndef main():\n    now = datetime.now()\n    is_morning = len(sys.argv) > 1 and sys.argv[1] == \"morning\"\n    label = \"🌅 早间版\" if is_morning else \"📘 晚间版\"\n\n    print(f\"\\n{'='*60}\")\n    print(f\"📡 微博财经大V监控 - {label}\")\n    print(f\"⏰ {now.strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')}\")\n    print(f\"{'='*60}\\n\")\n\n    REPORT_DIR.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n\n    # 1. 抓取\n    print(\"📡 抓取各KOL微博...\\n\")\n    results = fetch_all_kols()\n\n    # 2. 保存报告\n    report_file = REPORT_DIR / f\"report_{now.strftime('%Y%m%d_%H%M')}.txt\"\n    report_file.parent.mkdir(exist_ok=True)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":38,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n微博财经大V监控 - 定时推送脚本\n每天两次：08:30（盘前） 和 20:00（收盘后）\n\"\"\"\nimport json, subprocess, sys\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n# ── 配置 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nWORKSPACE = Path.home() / \".openclaw\" / \"workspace\"\nREPORT_DIR = WORKSPACE / \"weibo_monitor_reports\"\nSTATE_FILE = WORKSPACE / \"weibo_monitor_state.json\"\nCONFIG_FILE = WORKSPACE / \"config\" / \"investment_research_delivery_v1.json\"\n\nFEISHU_TARGET = \"chat:oc_8a819be3a90d35b8d0a2d5c1f4642b22\"  # 来福研讨会群\nOPENCLAW_BIN = str(Path.home() / \".local\" / \"share\" / \"fnm\" / \"aliases\" / \"default\" / \"bin\" / \"openclaw\")\n\nsys.path.insert(0, str(Path(__file__).parent))\nfrom fetch_and_report import fetch_all_kols, build_report, save_state\n\n# ── 工具 ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\ndef send_feishu(message: str, dry_run: bool = False) -> tuple:\n    cmd = [\n        OPENCLAW_BIN,\n        \"message\", \"send\",\n        \"--channel\", \"feishu\",\n        \"--target\", FEISHU_TARGET,\n        \"-m\", message,\n    ]\n    if dry_run:\n        cmd.append(\"--dry-run\")\n    try:\n        result = subprocess.run(cmd, capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=60)\n        return result.returncode == 0, result.stdout[:500] or result.stderr[:500]\n    except Exception as e:\n        return False, str(e)\n\n# ── 主程序 ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\ndef main():\n    now = datetime.now()\n    is_morning = len(sys.argv) > 1 and sys.argv[1] == \"morning\"\n    label = \"🌅 早间版\" if is_morning else \"📘 晚间版\"\n\n    print(f\"\\n{'='*60}\")\n    print(f\"📡 微博财经大V监控 - {label}\")\n    print(f\"⏰ {now.strftime('%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')}\")\n    print(f\"{'='*60}\\n\")\n\n    REPORT_DIR.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n\n    # 1. 抓取\n    print(\"📡 抓取各KOL微博...\\n\")\n    results = fetch_all_kols()\n\n    # 2. 保存报告\n    report_file = REPORT_DIR / f\"report_{now.strftime('%Y%m%d_%H%M')}.txt\"\n    report_file.parent.mkdir(exist_ok=True)","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774875220437}}
{"type":"message","id":"e7e525e3","parentId":"63bbcd28","timestamp":"2026-03-30T12:53:43.351Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me look at the `fetch_and_report.py` to understand the mcporter issue.","thinkingSignature":"5642962d81e247d6af4723017fa07f32b1d92248a45422adf7ea56ae8f530fb8"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_kiscajeleuu8_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"head -80 /Users/ling/workspace/weibo-monitor/fetch_and_report.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":36396,"output":62,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":61478,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774875220454,"responseId":"0619a554dea9375ab83528d1f0c7ed3f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b01f7f6f","parentId":"e7e525e3","timestamp":"2026-03-30T12:53:43.476Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_kiscajeleuu8_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n微博财经大V每日监控报告\n每天两次自动抓取 → 分析 → 推送飞书\n\"\"\"\nimport json\nimport subprocess\nimport re\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n# ── 配置 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nKOL_FILE = Path(__file__).parent / \"kol_uids.json\"\nSTATE_FILE = Path(__file__).parent / \"last_fetch.json\"\nMAX_PER_KOL = 20   # 每次最多抓取微博条数\nFEISHU_CHAT_ID = \"oc_8a819be3a90d35b8d0a2d5c1f4642b22\"  # 飞书群\n\n# 关键词过滤器：只保留包含这些词的微博（财经相关）\nFINANCE_KEYWORDS = [\n    \"股\", \"A股\", \"上证\", \"深证\", \"指数\", \"大盘\", \"牛市\", \"熊市\",\n    \"投资\", \"基金\", \"ETF\", \"私募\", \"公募\",\n    \"美联储\", \"降息\", \"加息\", \"汇率\", \"美元\", \"人民币\",\n    \"央行\", \"货币政策\", \"财政政策\",\n    \"GDP\", \"CPI\", \"PPI\", \"经济\",\n    \"房地产\", \"房价\", \"楼市\",\n    \"科技\", \"AI\", \"半导体\", \"芯片\",\n    \"新能源\", \"锂\", \"光伏\", \"电动车\",\n    \"黄金\", \"原油\", \"大宗商品\",\n    \"港股\", \"美股\", \"道琼斯\", \"纳斯达克\", \"标普\",\n    \"汇市\", \"债市\", \"银行\", \"保险\",\n    \"监管\", \"政策\", \"会议\", \"讲话\",\n    \"IPO\", \"上市\", \"定增\", \"减持\", \"回购\",\n    \"业绩\", \"财报\", \"年报\", \"季报\",\n]\n\n# ── 工具函数 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\ndef call_weibo(uid: int, limit: int = MAX_PER_KOL) -> list:\n    \"\"\"调用 mcp-server-weibo 获取某用户最新微博\"\"\"\n    cmd = [\"mcporter\", \"call\", \"weibo.get_feeds\", f\"uid={uid}\", f\"limit={limit}\"]\n    try:\n        result = subprocess.run(cmd, capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=30)\n        if result.returncode != 0:\n            return []\n        data = json.loads(result.stdout)\n        return data if isinstance(data, list) else []\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"  ⚠️ 获取UID {uid} 失败: {e}\")\n        return []\n\ndef parse_time(time_str: str) -> datetime:\n    \"\"\"解析微博时间字符串\"\"\"\n    # 格式: \"Mon Mar 23 15:28:32 +0800 2026\"\n    try:\n        return datetime.strptime(time_str, \"%a %b %d %H:%M:%S +0800 %Y\")\n    except:\n        try:\n            # 格式: \"2026-03-23 15:28:32\"\n            return datetime.strptime(time_str[:19], \"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")\n        except:\n            return None\n\ndef is_today(dt: datetime) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"判断是否今天或昨天的微博\"\"\"\n    if dt is None:\n        return True  # 无法解析的默认保留\n    now = datetime.now()\n    today_start = now.replace(hour=0, minute=0, second=0, microsecond=0)\n    yesterday_start = today_start - timedelta(days=1)\n    return dt >= yesterday_start\n\ndef clean_text(html_text: str) -> str:\n    \"\"\"清洗HTML标签，提取纯文本\"\"\"\n    # 移除 <a href=...> 及其内容\n    text = re.sub(r'<a[^>]*>.*?</a>', '', html_text, flags=re.DOTALL)\n    # 移除 HTML 标签\n    text = re.sub(r'<[^>]+>', '', text)\n    # 移除多余空白\n    text = re.sub(r'\\s+', ' ', text).strip()\n    return text"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":47,"aggregated":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n微博财经大V每日监控报告\n每天两次自动抓取 → 分析 → 推送飞书\n\"\"\"\nimport json\nimport subprocess\nimport re\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n# ── 配置 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nKOL_FILE = Path(__file__).parent / \"kol_uids.json\"\nSTATE_FILE = Path(__file__).parent / \"last_fetch.json\"\nMAX_PER_KOL = 20   # 每次最多抓取微博条数\nFEISHU_CHAT_ID = \"oc_8a819be3a90d35b8d0a2d5c1f4642b22\"  # 飞书群\n\n# 关键词过滤器：只保留包含这些词的微博（财经相关）\nFINANCE_KEYWORDS = [\n    \"股\", \"A股\", \"上证\", \"深证\", \"指数\", \"大盘\", \"牛市\", \"熊市\",\n    \"投资\", \"基金\", \"ETF\", \"私募\", \"公募\",\n    \"美联储\", \"降息\", \"加息\", \"汇率\", \"美元\", \"人民币\",\n    \"央行\", \"货币政策\", \"财政政策\",\n    \"GDP\", \"CPI\", \"PPI\", \"经济\",\n    \"房地产\", \"房价\", \"楼市\",\n    \"科技\", \"AI\", \"半导体\", \"芯片\",\n    \"新能源\", \"锂\", \"光伏\", \"电动车\",\n    \"黄金\", \"原油\", \"大宗商品\",\n    \"港股\", \"美股\", \"道琼斯\", \"纳斯达克\", \"标普\",\n    \"汇市\", \"债市\", \"银行\", \"保险\",\n    \"监管\", \"政策\", \"会议\", \"讲话\",\n    \"IPO\", \"上市\", \"定增\", \"减持\", \"回购\",\n    \"业绩\", \"财报\", \"年报\", \"季报\",\n]\n\n# ── 工具函数 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n\ndef call_weibo(uid: int, limit: int = MAX_PER_KOL) -> list:\n    \"\"\"调用 mcp-server-weibo 获取某用户最新微博\"\"\"\n    cmd = [\"mcporter\", \"call\", \"weibo.get_feeds\", f\"uid={uid}\", f\"limit={limit}\"]\n    try:\n        result = subprocess.run(cmd, capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=30)\n        if result.returncode != 0:\n            return []\n        data = json.loads(result.stdout)\n        return data if isinstance(data, list) else []\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"  ⚠️ 获取UID {uid} 失败: {e}\")\n        return []\n\ndef parse_time(time_str: str) -> datetime:\n    \"\"\"解析微博时间字符串\"\"\"\n    # 格式: \"Mon Mar 23 15:28:32 +0800 2026\"\n    try:\n        return datetime.strptime(time_str, \"%a %b %d %H:%M:%S +0800 %Y\")\n    except:\n        try:\n            # 格式: \"2026-03-23 15:28:32\"\n            return datetime.strptime(time_str[:19], \"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")\n        except:\n            return None\n\ndef is_today(dt: datetime) -> bool:\n    \"\"\"判断是否今天或昨天的微博\"\"\"\n    if dt is None:\n        return True  # 无法解析的默认保留\n    now = datetime.now()\n    today_start = now.replace(hour=0, minute=0, second=0, microsecond=0)\n    yesterday_start = today_start - timedelta(days=1)\n    return dt >= yesterday_start\n\ndef clean_text(html_text: str) -> str:\n    \"\"\"清洗HTML标签，提取纯文本\"\"\"\n    # 移除 <a href=...> 及其内容\n    text = re.sub(r'<a[^>]*>.*?</a>', '', html_text, flags=re.DOTALL)\n    # 移除 HTML 标签\n    text = re.sub(r'<[^>]+>', '', text)\n    # 移除多余空白\n    text = re.sub(r'\\s+', ' ', text).strip()\n    return text","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774875223461}}
{"type":"message","id":"5fed11f5","parentId":"b01f7f6f","timestamp":"2026-03-30T12:53:59.366Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is clear now:\n1. `mcporter` is called as a bare command without the full path in `fetch_and_report.py`\n2. The cron job runs in a minimal PATH environment where neither `/Users/ling/.local/share/fnm/node-versions/v22.22.0/installation/bin` nor the fnm aliases path are included\n\nThe fix:\n1. Change `mcporter` in `fetch_and_report.py` to use the full path: `/Users/ling/.local/share/fnm/node-versions/v22.22.0/installation/bin/mcporter`\n2. For the node issue, the cron script uses `OPENCLAW_BIN` which is the openclaw binary path, not the node path. \n\nLooking at the actual error in the log, `env: node: No such file or directory` suggests the `send_feishu` function is trying to run `openclaw message send` but the node environment isn't available in the cron job's PATH. The subprocess call is likely spawning a shell that can't find node. I need to either ensure the full PATH is set in the cron job's environment or use the full path to node when invoking openclaw.\n\nFor the `mcporter` issue, it's a Node.js script so it needs the full path to the mcporter binary in the cron environment. Let me check the cron entry to see what PATH is actually being used.\n\nThe issue is that `mcporter` in `fetch_and_report.py` needs to be invoked with the full path, and the `OPENCLAW_BIN` variable in `cron_weibo_monitor.py` should point to the actual openclaw binary, not node. I need to verify what the correct path is for the openclaw binary and whether node is even being called directly or through openclaw. Looking at the error chain, the `send_feishu` function runs `openclaw message send`, which internally needs `node` in its PATH. The cron job's minimal environment doesn't have access to the full PATH, so I need to add it when invoking the openclaw binary rather than relying on the system's node installation.","thinkingSignature":"5ed1d2f1ac63701defe61425e96bff5d74a9234a893e0c41288957e52f75063e"},{"type":"text","text":"问题明确了：`cron_weibo_monitor.py` 调用 `openclaw message send` 时，cron 的执行环境 PATH 不含 node 路径；同时 `fetch_and_report.py` 调用 `mcporter` 也缺路径。两处都要修。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3ubt3v82v6u4_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"grep -n \"OPENCLAW_BIN\\|mcporter\\|subprocess\\|PATH\" /Users/ling/workspace/weibo-monitor/cron_weibo_monitor.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":37344,"output":544,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62908,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774875223476,"responseId":"0619a557216e2ccd1c1e6ec7e1b44af4"}}
