{"type":"message","id":"41f68e47","parentId":"7628ce61","timestamp":"2026-03-30T12:55:44.960Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The report is now successfully generated and pushed to Feishu. Let me summarize what was fixed.","thinkingSignature":"970794cbadca79a999cb6bcdfdc8299bdcc9e1b250e2051945c341cc5433b12a"},{"type":"text","text":"今晚的简报已成功生成并推送飞书 ✅\n\n---\n\n**修复内容：**\n\n| 文件 | 问题 | 修复 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `fetch_and_report.py` | `mcporter` 无全路径，cron 环境找不到 | 改为 fnm 全路径 `/Users/ling/.local/share/fnm/node-versions/v22.22.0/installation/bin/mcporter` |\n| `cron_weibo_monitor.py` | `openclaw` shebang 是 `#!/usr/bin/env node`，cron PATH 不含 node | `subprocess.run` 加 `env` 参数，显式补全 fnm bin 到 PATH |\n\n**今晚战况：** 10位大V，33条财经内容。\n- 重点：wu2198 认为短线支持在3850点、关注3957反击；杨德龙喊话长线慢牛；洪榕说能源+AI+金融是中美三大决战高地；唐史主任司马迁提到军工/半导体/数字要素机会。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42789,"output":233,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":68042,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774875332654,"responseId":"0619a5c4f8e65904a0417bf7e6794282"}}
