{"type":"message","id":"defb664d","parentId":"12343e07","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:02:19.671Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Found it. The script uses `shutil.which(\"openclaw\")` and then `[\"openclaw\", \"message\", \"send\", ...]`. In cron, the PATH doesn't include fnm's node-versions bin directory where `openclaw` is symlinked. Let me look at the full code to understand how it works and fix it.","thinkingSignature":"ffbb7b23207f20b36d2baa5c42bfe87435371aff7f9537f3d2913f040540a1f7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_mdkfatkw6h1k_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '20,50p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/push_breadth_strict_oos_paper_to_feishu.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":50234,"output":142,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75396,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774875734499,"responseId":"0619a75676ff5053cd834de864f46911"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e313b8b3","parentId":"defb664d","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:02:19.780Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_mdkfatkw6h1k_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def write_json(path: Path, payload: dict) -> None:\n    path.write_text(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n\n\ndef push(message: str) -> tuple[bool, str]:\n    cmd = [\n        \"openclaw\", \"message\", \"send\",\n        \"--channel\", \"feishu\",\n        \"--account\", \"main\",\n        \"--target\", \"user:ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080\",\n        \"-m\", message,\n    ]\n    proc = subprocess.run(cmd, capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=120)\n    detail = ((proc.stdout or \"\").strip() or (proc.stderr or \"\").strip())[-2000:]\n    return proc.returncode == 0, detail\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    summary = load_json(SUMMARY_PATH)\n    if not summary:\n        raise SystemExit(\"missing breadth_strict_oos_paper_latest.json\")\n    dedupe = f\"{summary.get('signal_date')}|{summary.get('nav')}|{summary.get('position_count')}|{','.join(summary.get('buy_list', []))}|{','.join(summary.get('sell_list', []))}\"\n    prev = load_json(STATE_PATH)\n    if prev.get(\"dedupe\") == dedupe:\n        print(json.dumps({\"status\": \"SKIPPED\", \"reason\": \"duplicate\"}, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n        return\n    message = \"\\n\".join([\n        f\"严格样本外宽度策略模拟盘｜{summary.get('generated_at')}\",\n        f\"信号日期: {summary.get('signal_date')}\",\n        f\"净值: {summary.get('nav')}\",\n        f\"总资产: {summary.get('total_value')}\","}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":31,"aggregated":"def write_json(path: Path, payload: dict) -> None:\n    path.write_text(json.dumps(payload, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2), encoding=\"utf-8\")\n\n\ndef push(message: str) -> tuple[bool, str]:\n    cmd = [\n        \"openclaw\", \"message\", \"send\",\n        \"--channel\", \"feishu\",\n        \"--account\", \"main\",\n        \"--target\", \"user:ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080\",\n        \"-m\", message,\n    ]\n    proc = subprocess.run(cmd, capture_output=True, text=True, timeout=120)\n    detail = ((proc.stdout or \"\").strip() or (proc.stderr or \"\").strip())[-2000:]\n    return proc.returncode == 0, detail\n\n\ndef main() -> None:\n    summary = load_json(SUMMARY_PATH)\n    if not summary:\n        raise SystemExit(\"missing breadth_strict_oos_paper_latest.json\")\n    dedupe = f\"{summary.get('signal_date')}|{summary.get('nav')}|{summary.get('position_count')}|{','.join(summary.get('buy_list', []))}|{','.join(summary.get('sell_list', []))}\"\n    prev = load_json(STATE_PATH)\n    if prev.get(\"dedupe\") == dedupe:\n        print(json.dumps({\"status\": \"SKIPPED\", \"reason\": \"duplicate\"}, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n        return\n    message = \"\\n\".join([\n        f\"严格样本外宽度策略模拟盘｜{summary.get('generated_at')}\",\n        f\"信号日期: {summary.get('signal_date')}\",\n        f\"净值: {summary.get('nav')}\",\n        f\"总资产: {summary.get('total_value')}\",","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774875739765}}
{"type":"message","id":"fa5b775c","parentId":"e313b8b3","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:02:36.248Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The fix is straightforward - the script uses `subprocess.run` with `[\"openclaw\", ...]` but without an explicit PATH. In cron, the fnm node bin is not in PATH. I need to modify the subprocess call to include the proper PATH, or change the command to use the full path.\n\nLet me also check `push_control_tower_alert_if_changed.py`.\n\nThe best fix is to update `cron_python.sh` to prepend the fnm node bin to PATH before running Python scripts. Or I can fix each individual Python script.\n\nActually, the cleanest fix is to update `cron_python.sh` to set the PATH correctly. Let me check what PATH is needed.\n\n\nI see that `NEWS_MARKET_0850` already has the correct PATH set in cron, but the weibo-monitor script needed manual fixes for `openclaw` and `mcporter` calls, and `breadth_strict_oos_paper_cron` is running through `cron_python.sh` which doesn't include the fnm node bin in its PATH.\n\nI'll update `cron_python.sh` to prepend the fnm node bin to the PATH so that `openclaw` can be found when these cron jobs execute.","thinkingSignature":"7b69a21a879f7cae15a876cce3ecee67a211e69b6caeeee00e26b58e53151b16"},{"type":"text","text":"根因清楚了：`cron_python.sh` 里的 `exec \"$PYTHON_REAL\" \"$@\"` 执行时，Python 子进程继承的 PATH 没有 fnm 的 node bin，导致调 `openclaw` 的脚本全失败。修 `cron_python.sh` 加 PATH：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_349jch3jvob2_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"old_text":"PYTHON_BIN=\"${QUANT_CRON_PYTHON:-$DEFAULT_PYTHON_BIN}\"\nif ! command -v \"$PYTHON_BIN\" >/dev/null 2>&1; then\n  echo \"[RUNTIME] status=ERROR reason=python_not_found python=${PYTHON_BIN}\"\n  exit 127\nfi","newText":"PYTHON_BIN=\"${QUANT_CRON_PYTHON:-$DEFAULT_PYTHON_BIN}\"\n# cron 环境 PATH 不含 fnm node 路径，需要显式补全\nFNM_BIN=\"${HOME}/.local/share/fnm/node-versions/v22.22.0/installation/bin\"\nif [[ \":$PATH:\" != *\":${FNM_BIN}:\"* ]]; then\n