{"type":"message","id":"56f5cb46","parentId":"3ea01ee7","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:12:48.535Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the template. I'll create probe_guard configs for the 5 missing profiles, then add them to the cron. Let me think about appropriate thresholds for each:\n\n1. **exit_dual** - dual threshold exit strategy paper, moderate risk:\n   - paper_max_drawdown_pct: 8.0 (same as balanced)\n   - paper_20d_return_floor_pct: -5.0\n   - paper_20d_sharpe_floor: -0.1\n   - paper_avg_slippage_cap: 200.0\n   - paper_avg_turnover_cap: 0.12\n   - paper_position_deviation_cap: 0.15\n\n2. **exit_tight** - tight threshold exit strategy paper:\n   - paper_max_drawdown_pct: 8.0\n   - paper_20d_return_floor_pct: -5.0\n   - paper_20d_sharpe_floor: -0.1\n   - paper_avg_slippage_cap: 200.0\n   - paper_avg_turnover_cap: 0.12\n   - paper_position_deviation_cap: 0.15\n\n3. **alpha55** - alpha55 strategy paper:\n   - paper_max_drawdown_pct: 10.0\n   - paper_20d_return_floor_pct: -5.0\n   - paper_20d_sharpe_floor: -0.1\n   - paper_avg_slippage_cap: 200.0\n   - paper_avg_turnover_cap: 0.12\n   - paper_position_deviation_cap: 0.20\n\n4. **breadth_strict_oos** - breadth strategy with stricter constraints:\n   - paper_max_drawdown_pct: 15.0\n   - paper_20d_return_floor_pct: -8.0\n   - paper_20d_sharpe_floor: -0.2\n   - paper_avg_slippage_cap: 250.0\n   - paper_avg_turnover_cap: 0.20\n   - paper_position_deviation_cap: 0.30\n\n5. **breadth_aggressive** - most aggressive breadth approach with higher drawdown tolerance and elevated turnover targets:\n   - paper_max_drawdown_pct: 18.0\n   - paper_20d_return_floor_pct: -10.0\n   - paper_20d_sharpe_floor: -0.2\n   - paper_avg_slippage_cap: 300.0\n   - paper_avg_turnover_cap: 0.22\n   - paper_position_deviation_cap: 0.35\n\nThe probe_guard_threshold values should be set relative to each strategy's actual risk tolerance rather than using defaults, since the breadth strategies already show elevated volatility and drawdown.","thinkingSignature":"7fba1a6c6af4f208718d6b0415eef52e56b4df7c3bc08e11b0fb9dbabbf6bdb2"},{"type":"text","text":"现在创建 5 个缺失的 probe_guard config：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_emixrzjpv4ly_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"{\n  \"strategy_id\": \"breadth_probe_guard_exit_dual_v1\",\n  \"profile_slug\": \"exit_dual\",\n  \"profile_name\": \"双阈退出验证盘\",\n  \"feishu\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n    \"account\": \"main\",\n    \"target_user\": \"user:ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080\"\n  },\n  \"thresholds\": {\n    \"paper_max_drawdown_pct\": 10.0,\n    \"paper_20d_return_floor_pct\": -6.0,\n    \"paper_20d_sharpe_floor\": -0.1,\n    \"paper_avg_slippage_cap\": 200.0,\n    \"paper_avg_turnover_cap\": 0.12,\n    \"paper_position_deviation_cap\": 0.15,\n    \"paper_missing_journal_records_cap\": 0,\n    \"paper_error_trade_count_cap\": 0\n  },\n  \"admission\": {\n    \"paper_observation_min_days\": 20,\n    \"paper_observation_target_days\": 40,\n    \"probe_capital_pct_min\": 1.0,\n    \"probe_capital_pct_max\": 5.0\n  }\n}\n","file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/config/strategy_probe_guard_exit_dual_v1.json"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_emixrzjpv4ly_2","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"{\n  \"strategy_id\": \"breadth_probe_guard_exit_tight_v1\",\n  \"profile_slug\": \"exit_tight\",\n  \"profile_name\": \"紧阈退出验证盘\",\n  \"feishu\": {\n    \"enabled\": true,\n    \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n    \"account\": \"main\",\n    \"target_user\": \"user:ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080\"\n  },\n  \"thresholds\": {\n    \"paper_max_drawdown_pct\": 10.0,\n    \"paper_20d_return_floor_pct\": -6.0,\n    \"paper_20d_sharpe_floor\": -0.1,\n    \"paper_avg_slippage_cap\": 200.0,\n    \"paper_avg_turnover_cap\": 0.12,\n    \"paper_position_deviation_cap\": 0.15,\n    \"paper_missing_journal_records_cap\": 0,\n    \"paper_error_trade