{"type":"message","id":"60fd7f9f","parentId":"3302ee4b","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:13:17.573Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The panels are still generating. Let me wait for them and in the meantime, check the `balanced` issue where the abnormal item is 'none' but status is YELLOW. Let me look at how the status is determined for balanced.","thinkingSignature":"d20d1251c8eeacf4af98cae17fd271e147cf07068df1a57fc73862cf2296ce4a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_ev8i532rcyqk_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '60,95p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/generate_strategy_performance_panel.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":78942,"output":109,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104071,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774876391438,"responseId":"0619a9e8366c47582a100b0faf982b88"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c8d32dfd","parentId":"60fd7f9f","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:13:17.674Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ev8i532rcyqk_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def freshness_label(age_hours: float | None, *, stale_hours: int = 24) -> tuple[str, bool]:\n    if age_hours is None:\n        return \"缺失\", True\n    if age_hours > stale_hours:\n        return f\"停更 {age_hours:.1f}h\", True\n    return f\"正常 {age_hours:.1f}h\", False\n\n\ndef apply_stale_override(status: str, status_label: str, reasons: list[str], age_hours: float | None) -> tuple[str, str, list[str]]:\n    _, is_stale = freshness_label(age_hours)\n    if not is_stale:\n        return status, status_label, reasons\n    reasons = list(reasons)\n    reasons.append(\"stale_file\")\n    if status == \"GREEN\":\n        return \"YELLOW\", \"STALE\", reasons\n    if status == \"NO_DATA\" and status_label == \"LEGACY\":\n        return status, status_label, reasons\n    return status, status_label, reasons\n\n\ndef infer_account_status(profile_slug: str, account: dict[str, Any], guard: dict[str, Any]) -> tuple[str, str, list[str]]:\n    if not account:\n        return \"NO_DATA\", \"NO_DATA\", [\"missing_account\"]\n\n    guard_status = str(guard.get(\"status\") or \"\").strip().upper()\n    if guard_status in STATUS_ORDER:\n        reasons = [str(item.get(\"code\") or \"\").strip() for item in (guard.get(\"issues\") or []) if str(item.get(\"code\") or \"\").strip()]\n        return guard_status, guard_status, reasons\n\n    if profile_slug in CURRENT_PAPER_SLUGS:\n        return \"YELLOW\", \"UNGUARDED\", [\"missing_probe_guard\"]\n    if profile_slug in LEGACY_PAPER_SLUGS:\n        return \"NO_DATA\", \"LEGACY\", [\"legacy_profile\"]"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":28,"aggregated":"def freshness_label(age_hours: float | None, *, stale_hours: int = 24) -> tuple[str, bool]:\n    if age_hours is None:\n        return \"缺失\", True\n    if age_hours > stale_hours:\n        return f\"停更 {age_hours:.1f}h\", True\n    return f\"正常 {age_hours:.1f}h\", False\n\n\ndef apply_stale_override(status: str, status_label: str, reasons: list[str], age_hours: float | None) -> tuple[str, str, list[str]]:\n    _, is_stale = freshness_label(age_hours)\n    if not is_stale:\n        return status, status_label, reasons\n    reasons = list(reasons)\n    reasons.append(\"stale_file\")\n    if status == \"GREEN\":\n        return \"YELLOW\", \"STALE\", reasons\n    if status == \"NO_DATA\" and status_label == \"LEGACY\":\n        return status, status_label, reasons\n    return status, status_label, reasons\n\n\ndef infer_account_status(profile_slug: str, account: dict[str, Any], guard: dict[str, Any]) -> tuple[str, str, list[str]]:\n    if not account:\n        return \"NO_DATA\", \"NO_DATA\", [\"missing_account\"]\n\n    guard_status = str(guard.get(\"status\") or \"\").strip().upper()\n    if guard_status in STATUS_ORDER:\n        reasons = [str(item.get(\"code\") or \"\").strip() for item in (guard.get(\"issues\") or []) if str(item.get(\"code\") or \"\").strip()]\n        return guard_status, guard_status, reasons\n\n    if profile_slug in CURRENT_PAPER_SLUGS:\n        return \"YELLOW\", \"UNGUARDED\", [\"missing_probe_guard\"]\n    if profile_slug in LEGACY_PAPER_SLUGS:\n        return \"NO_DATA\", \"LEGACY\", [\"legacy_profile\"]","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774876397661}}
{"type":"message","id":"bc7e7fa8","parentId":"c8d32dfd","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:13:26.655Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I see the issue with `balanced` having `none` but still being YELLOW. Looking at the logic:\n\nThe `infer_account_status` function first checks if there's a `guard` (probe guard) file. If `guard_status in STATUS_ORDER`, it returns the guard's status and reasons. If not, and the profile is in `CURRENT_PAPER_SLUGS`, it returns YELLOW with `missing_probe_guard`.\n\nSince balanced HAS a probe_guard file, the guard status should be returned. But looking at the HTML, balanced shows `issues=none` but still YELLOW. This means the guard file exists but returned a YELLOW status (which is not \"GREEN\" but \"YELLOW\" is in STATUS_ORDER).\n \nSo the guard file for balanced is probably returning a YELLOW status without any issue codes attached, which explains why the display shows `none` while the status remains YELLOW.","thinkingSignature":"7090cc0b2c33da809c7edc04ac05d7331160d74be0c927e172f1aad34a36cfd7"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_yr12wa40uizf_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_balanced_probe_guard_latest.json | python3 -m json.tool | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":79468,"output":253,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104741,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774876397675,"responseId":"0619a9ed03c7073ca58ce5f167007f41"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e265aaf3","parentId":"bc7e7fa8","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:13:26.777Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_yr12wa40uizf_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n    \"generated_at\": \"2026-03-30 21:12:59\",\n    \"config\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/config/strategy_probe_guard_balanced_v1.json\",\n    \"date_tag\": \"20260330\",\n    \"profile_slug\": \"balanced\",\n    \"status\": \"YELLOW\",\n    \"tomorrow_mode\": \"observe\",\n    \"issues\": [],\n    \"inputs\": {\n        \"journal\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_balanced_trading_journal_20260330.csv\",\n        \"orders\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_balanced_orders_v1_20260330.csv\",\n        \"account\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_balanced_account_v1_latest.json\",\n        \"metrics\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_balanced_trading_metrics_20260330.json\",\n        \"positions\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_balanced_portfolio_positions_latest.csv\"\n    },\n    \"stats\": {\n        \"nav\": 994607.97,\n        \"planned_orders\": 13,\n        \"journal_records\": 1,\n        \"position_count\": 3,\n        \"max_drawdown_pct\": 0.72,\n        \"trailing_20d_return_pct\": 0.18,\n        \"trailing_20d_sharpe\": 0.0,\n        \"avg_slippage\": 7.32,\n        \"avg_turnover_proxy\": 0.0,\n        \"error_trade_count\": 0\n    },\n    \"push\": {\n        \"ok\": true,\n        \"detail\": \"[plugins] feishu_doc: Registered feishu_doc, feishu_app_scopes\\n[plugins] feishu_chat: Registered feishu_chat tool\\n[plugin