{"type":"message","id":"d6d34ba3","parentId":"d5549774","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:16:46.979Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me also fix the same issue in line 165 of run_close_review_v1.py. But actually, let me first check whether the issue is actually in `run_strategy_probe_guard.py` or in `generate_strategy_probe_daily_reconciliation.py`.\n\nActually, looking at the error message again:\n```\nAttributeError: 'numpy.float64' object has no attribute 'fillna'\n```\nThis happens at line 130 in `run_strategy_probe_guard.py` which I've now fixed.\n\nBut wait - line 130 now has:\n```\ndaily_ret = pd.to_numeric(daily_ret_raw, errors=\"coerce\").fillna(0.0)\n\n\n```\n\nBut `daily_ret_raw` could be a numpy.float64 (a scalar). And `pd.to_numeric(scalar)` returns a scalar. And scalars don't have `fillna`. But I've now fixed this with the isinstance check.\n\nOK, let me now also check the `generate_strategy_probe_daily_reconciliation.py` line 165 which also has fillna.","thinkingSignature":"7782e24fde032724af8c2b895d2ed96fc88be5a4ad1cc9288578f846fedf447d"},{"type":"text","text":"同样检查另一处 `fillna`：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_3s8od8wstu5y_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '160,170p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/generate_strategy_probe_daily_reconciliation.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":82547,"output":277,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107844,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774876598490,"responseId":"0619aab68ded39c8f04abcc60f2bb436"}}
{"type":"message","id":"90a03bd8","parentId":"d6d34ba3","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:16:47.087Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_3s8od8wstu5y_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def build_summary(journal_df: pd.DataFrame, positions_df: pd.DataFrame, account_payload: dict[str, Any], metrics_payload: dict[str, Any]) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    action = journal_df.get(\"action\", pd.Series(dtype=str)).astype(str).str.upper() if not journal_df.empty else pd.Series(dtype=str)\n    buy_count = int((action == \"BUY\").sum()) if not action.empty else 0\n    sell_count = int((action == \"SELL\").sum()) if not action.empty else 0\n    slippage_mean = round(float(pd.to_numeric(journal_df.get(\"slippage\"), errors=\"coerce\").fillna(0.0).mean()), 2) if not journal_df.empty else 0.0\n    drawdown_min = round(abs(float(pd.to_numeric(journal_df.get(\"drawdown\"), errors=\"coerce\").dropna().min())), 2) if not journal_df.empty and pd.to_numeric(journal_df.get(\"drawdown\"), errors=\"coerce\").dropna().size else 0.0\n    metrics = metrics_payload.get(\"metrics\", {}) or {}\n    return {\n        \"position_count\": int(account_payload.get(\"position_count\", len(positions_df)) or 0),\n        \"cash\": round(parse_float(account_payload.get(\"cash\"), 0.0), 2),"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":29,"aggregated":"def build_summary(journal_df: pd.DataFrame, positions_df: pd.DataFrame, account_payload: dict[str, Any], metrics_payload: dict[str, Any]) -> dict[str, Any]:\n    action = journal_df.get(\"action\", pd.Series(dtype=str)).astype(str).str.upper() if not journal_df.empty else pd.Series(dtype=str)\n    buy_count = int((action == \"BUY\").sum()) if not action.empty else 0\n    sell_count = int((action == \"SELL\").sum()) if not action.empty else 0\n    slippage_mean = round(float(pd.to_numeric(journal_df.get(\"slippage\"), errors=\"coerce\").fillna(0.0).mean()), 2) if not journal_df.empty else 0.0\n    drawdown_min = round(abs(float(pd.to_numeric(journal_df.get(\"drawdown\"), errors=\"coerce\").dropna().min())), 2) if not journal_df.empty and pd.to_numeric(journal_df.get(\"drawdown\"), errors=\"coerce\").dropna().size else 0.0\n    metrics = metrics_payload.get(\"metrics\", {}) or {}\n    return {\n        \"position_count\": int(account_payload.get(\"position_count\", len(positions_df)) or 0),\n        \"cash\": round(parse_float(account_payload.get(\"cash\"), 0.0), 2),","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774876607072}}
{"type":"message","id":"56bdb6be","parentId":"90a03bd8","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:16:56.428Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The `slippage_mean` line at 165 could also fail if `journal_df.get(\"slippage\")` returns a scalar. Let me fix it similarly.","thinkingSignature":"f10cb00b1b1ba27d390f18007a0c151e2b2534214a67c4e0a812f247fd77dede"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_588oaduzlvzf_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"old_text":"    slippage_mean = round(float(pd.to_numeric(journal_df.get(\"slippage\"), errors=\"coerce\").fillna(0.0).mean()), 2) if not journal_df.empty else 0.0\n    drawdown_min = round(abs(float(pd.to_numeric(journal_df.get(\"drawdown\"), errors=\"coerce\").dropna().min())), 2) if not journal_df.empty and pd.to_numeric(journal_df.get(\"drawdown\"), errors=\"coerce\").dropna().size else 0.0","newText":"    slippage_raw = journal_df.get(\"slippage\") if not journal_df.empty else None\n    slippage_series = pd.Series([slippage_raw]) if isinstance(slippage_raw, (int, float)) else (pd.to_numeric(slippage_raw, errors=\"coerce\").fillna(0.0) if slippage_raw is not None else pd.Series([], dtype=float))\n    slippage_mean = round(float(slippage_series.mean()), 2) if len(slippage_series) else 0.0\n    drawdown_raw = journal_df.get(\"drawdown\") if not journal_df.empty else None\n    drawdown_series = pd.Series([drawdown_raw]) if isinstance(drawdown_raw, (int, float)) else (pd.to_numeric(drawdown_raw, errors=\"coerce\").dropna() if drawdown_raw is not None else pd.Series([], dtype=float))\n    drawdown_min = round(abs(float(drawdown_series.min())), 2) if len(drawdown_series) else 0.0","file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/generate_strategy_probe_daily_reconciliation.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":83128,"output":439,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":108587,"cost":{"input":0,"outp