{"type":"message","id":"73b3ca17","parentId":"d6362be4","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:19:48.229Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"`trailing_20d_return_pct: -0.08` and threshold is `paper_20d_return_floor_pct: -5.0`. So -0.08 < -5.0 is False (since -0.08 is greater than -5.0, it's not a breach).\n\n`trailing_20d_sharpe: 0.0` and threshold is `paper_20d_sharpe_floor: 0.0`. So 0.0 < 0.0 is False (not a breach).\n\n`max_drawdown_pct: 0.72` and threshold is `paper_max_drawdown_pct: 8.0`. \n\nSince 0.72 < 8.0, there's no breach either. But the guard is reporting YELLOW status—let me check what conditions are actually triggering that warning, since the threshold checks don't seem to be the culprit.\n\nLooking at the code around line 88, if the guard status is in STATUS_ORDER, it should return that status directly. The YELLOW must be coming from somewhere else in the guard logic itself, not from threshold violations. I'm tracing through the function logic more carefully now. The guard_status is \"YELLOW\", which is in STATUS_ORDER, so it returns immediately without checking the `CURRENT_PAPER_SLUGS` condition. But there's likely a secondary status determination happening that's causing the YELLOW. Looking at the broader context of lines 88-95, I need to understand how the status flows through the entire conditional chain rather than just the first branch. Looking at the balanced probe guard output, it returned \"YELLOW\" with an empty issues list, which suggests the guard is evaluating to YELLOW status. Since balanced isn't in LEGACY_PAPER_SLUGS, the status determination must be coming from elsewhere in the logic. Let me trace through what conditions could produce YELLOW with no issues listed. I need to trace through the `infer_account_status` function more carefully to understand why `balanced` is returning YELLOW when the issues list is empty.","thinkingSignature":"c09350f3e132e5ae98f6e84bb42bbfb6933269f274c0bd58a6d886445d644f6e"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_0hwv9w08cwhk_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sed -n '55,120p' /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/generate_strategy_performance_panel.py"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":90222,"output":488,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115730,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774876768710,"responseId":"0619ab6048766e93e16b412e59761b26"}}
{"type":"message","id":"279fe257","parentId":"73b3ca17","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:19:48.362Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_0hwv9w08cwhk_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"def file_age_hours(path: Path | None) -> float | None:\n    if not path or not path.exists():\n        return None\n    return max((datetime.now() - datetime.fromtimestamp(path.stat().st_mtime)).total_seconds() / 3600.0, 0.0)\n\n\ndef freshness_label(age_hours: float | None, *, stale_hours: int = 24) -> tuple[str, bool]:\n    if age_hours is None:\n        return \"缺失\", True\n    if age_hours > stale_hours:\n        return f\"停更 {age_hours:.1f}h\", True\n    return f\"正常 {age_hours:.1f}h\", False\n\n\ndef apply_stale_override(status: str, status_label: str, reasons: list[str], age_hours: float | None) -> tuple[str, str, list[str]]:\n    _, is_stale = freshness_label(age_hours)\n    if not is_stale:\n        return status, status_label, reasons\n    reasons = list(reasons)\n    reasons.append(\"stale_file\")\n    if status == \"GREEN\":\n        return \"YELLOW\", \"STALE\", reasons\n    if status == \"NO_DATA\" and status_label == \"LEGACY\":\n        return status, status_label, reasons\n    return status, status_label, reasons\n\n\ndef infer_account_status(profile_slug: str, account: dict[str, Any], guard: dict[str, Any]) -> tuple[str, str, list[str]]:\n    if not account:\n        return \"NO_DATA\", \"NO_DATA\", [\"missing_account\"]\n\n    guard_status = str(guard.get(\"status\") or \"\").strip().upper()\n    if guard_status in STATUS_ORDER:\n        reasons = [str(item.get(\"code\") or \"\").strip() for item in (guard.get(\"issues\") or []) if str(item.get(\"code\") or \"\").strip()]\n        return guard_status, guard_status, reasons\n\n    if profile_slug in CURRENT_PAPER_SLUGS:\n        return \"YELLOW\", \"UNGUARDED\", [\"missing_probe_guard\"]\n    if profile_slug in LEGACY_PAPER_SLUGS:\n        return \"NO_DATA\", \"LEGACY\", [\"legacy_profile\"]\n    return \"NO_DATA\", \"NO_DATA\", [\"missing_guard\"]\n\n\ndef build_curve_points(curve: pd.DataFrame, account: dict[str, Any]) -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\n    curve_points: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n    if not curve.empty:\n        for _, row in curve.iterrows():\n            curve_points.append(\n                {\n                    \"date\": str(row.get(\"date\", row.get(\"date_tag\", \"\"))),\n                    \"nav\": parse_float(row.get(\"nav\"), 0.0),\n                    \"drawdown_pct\": parse_float(row.get(\"drawdown_pct\"), 0.0),\n                }\n            )\n        return curve_points\n\n    latest_nav = parse_float(account.get(\"nav\"), 0.0)\n    initial_cash = parse_float(account.get(\"initial_cash\"), 0.0)\n    remaining_cash = parse_float(account.get(\"remaining_cash\"), 0.0)\n    total_cost = parse_float(account.get(\"total_cost\"), 0.0)\n    fallback_nav = latest_nav or (remaining_cash + total_cost)\n    if fallback_nav <= 0 and initial_cash > 0:\n        fallback_nav = initial_cash\n    if fallback_nav <= 0:\n        return []"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":34,"aggregated":"def file_age_hours(path: Path | None) -> float | None:\n    if not path or not path.exists():\n        return None\n    return max((datetime.now() - datetime.fromtimestamp(path.stat().st_mtime)).total_seconds() / 3600.0, 0.0)\n\n\ndef freshness_label(age_hours: float | None, *, stale_hours: int = 24) -> tuple[str, bool]:\n    if age_hours is None:\n        return \"缺失\", True\n    if age_hours > stale_hours:\n        return f\"停更 {age_hours:.1f}h\", True\n    return f\"正常 {age_hours:.1f}h\", False\n\n\ndef apply_stale_override(status: str, status_label: str, reasons: list[str], age_hours: float | None) -> tuple[str, str, list[str]]:\n    _, is_stale = freshness_label(age_hours)\n    if not is_stale:\n        return status, status_label, reasons\n    reasons = list(reasons)\n    reasons.append(\"stale_file\")\n    if status == \"GREEN\":\n        return \"YELLOW\", \"STALE\", reasons\n    if status == \"NO_DATA\" and status_label == \"LEGACY\":\n        return status, status_label, reasons\n    return status, status_label, reasons\n\n\ndef infer_account_status(profile_slug: str, account: dict[str, Any], guard: dict[str, Any]) -> tuple[str, str, list[str]]:\n    if not account:\n        return \"NO_DATA\", \"NO_DATA\", [\"missing_account\"]\n\n    guard_status = str(guard.get(\"status\") or \"\").strip().upper()\n    if guard_status in STATUS_ORDER:\n        reasons = [str(item.get(\"code\") or \"\").strip() for item in (guard.get(\"issues\") or []) if str(item.get(\"code\") or \"\").strip()]\n        return guard_status, guard_status, reasons\n\n    if profile_slug in CURRENT_PAPER_SLUGS:\n        return \"YELLOW\", \"UNGUARDED\", [\"missing_probe_guard\"]\n    if profile_slug in LEGACY_PAPER_SLUGS:\n        return \"NO_DATA\", \"LEGACY\", [\"legacy_profile\"]\n    return \"NO_DATA\", \"NO_DATA\", [\"missing_guard\"]\n\n\ndef build_curve_points(curve: pd.DataFrame, account: dict[str, Any]) -> list[dict[str, Any]]:\n    curve_points: list[dict[str, Any]] = []\n    if not curve.empty:\n        for _, row in curve.iterrows():\n            curve_points.append(\n                {\n                    \"date\": str(row.get(\"date\", row.get(\"date_tag\", \"\"))),\n                    \"nav\": parse_float(row.get(\"nav\"), 0.0),\n                    \"drawdown_pct\": parse_float(row.get(\"drawdown_pct\"), 0.0),\n                }\n            )\n        return curve_points\n\n    latest_nav = parse_float(account.get(\"nav\"), 0.0)\n    initial_cash = parse_float(account.get(\"initial_cash\"), 0.0)\n    remaining_cash = parse_float(account.get(\"remaining_cash\"), 0.0)\n    total_cost = parse_float(account.get(\"total_cost\"), 0.0)\n    fallback_nav = latest_nav or (remaining_cash + total_cost)\n    if fallback_nav <= 0 and initial_cash > 0:\n        fallback_nav = initial_cash\n    if fallback_nav <= 0:\n        return []","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774876788342}}
