{"type":"message","id":"f479f893","parentId":"b87741b7","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:24:15.967Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The breadth_strict_oos paper doesn't have a detailed positions file with cost information, and the holdings in the latest.json all show 0 cost. This means the system isn't tracking individual stock P&L for this strategy - only the overall NAV.\n\nThe key information I can provide:\n1. 10 holdings, all with 0 cost (data not tracked)\n2. Signal from 2026-03-03, 27 days stale\n3. Target 80% position, actual 31.2% - massive drift\n4. Overall NAV: 1.0051 (+0.51% from 1.0 baseline)\n\nThe return_pct for all holdings shows 0.00% because avg_cost is 0 - this is a data tracking gap in the breadth_strict_oos reporting, not actual zero returns.\n\n\nI should just report what I can actually verify from the available data rather than speculating about positions I can't confirm.","thinkingSignature":"4bbd3450c662c4dc6ecfa062969217f156e116ba3524b3aad389a3a70829f406"},{"type":"text","text":"持仓数据已拿到，但成本价全是 0——这是 breadth_strict_oos 报告的一个数据缺口，无法追踪单票浮盈。不过整体情况可以梳理清楚：\n\n---\n\n**严格样本外宽度策略持仓（信号日期：2026-03-03，已过期 27 天）**\n\n| 代码 | 名称 | 数量 | 现价 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|------|------|\n| 001330.SZ | | 4700 | 7.01 | 持有中 |\n| 600481.SH | | 4300 | 6.84 | 持有中 |\n| 600977.SH | | 2500 | 13.45 | 持有中 |\n| 603103.SH | | 1400 | 23.17 | 持有中 |\n| 603533.SH | | 1300 | 25.01 | 持有中 |\n| 688221.SH | | 1700 | 19.85 | 持有中 |\n| 688228.SH | | 300 | 105.57 | 持有中 |\n| 688435.SH | | 700 | 42.69 | 持有中 |\n| 688622.SH | | 300 | 91.00 | 持有中 |\n| 688699.SH | | 700 | 43.50 | 持有中 |\n\n**整体情况：**\n- 目标仓位：**80%**（80万）\n- 实际仓位：**31.2%**（约31万市值）\n- 现金：**69.1万**\n- 漂移：**-48.8%** → 触发 `POSITION_DRIFT_CRITICAL` 告警\n- 净值：1.0051（整体 **+0.51%**）\n- 策略状态：`signal_stale_hold`（信号过期，停止调仓）\n\n---\n\n**核心问题：** 预测文件最新只到 2026-03-03（27天前），此后没有新信号，所以既不卖出也不买入，仓位一直卡在 31%。需要刷新 `ml_predictions.csv` 或重新跑 Qlib 每日特征/预测流程，才能解锁新交易信号。\n\n要我帮你排查为什么预测文件停在了 03-03 吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-m