{"type":"message","id":"3c795627","parentId":"f7f76420","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:26:55.467Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Commit successful. Now the fix is done. The next time the push notification runs, it will include stock names.\n\nLet me summarize for the user.","thinkingSignature":"df5f651be01ef204c1dce22cbe450abe60af7fbdece0d224275d3c8db24b39ad"},{"type":"text","text":"\n已修复并提交 ✅\n\n修改内容：每次推送时通过 `akshare` 实时查询股票名称，结果缓存（最多200条），避免重复请求。\n\n**下次推送效果对比：**\n\n```\n# 修复前\n- 实际成交：\n  盘二 SELL 002565.SZ 600股 @15.2678\n\n# 修复后\n- 实际成交：\n  盘二 SELL 顺灏股份[002565.SZ] 600股 @15.2678\n```\n\n同理，被拦截候选股和各个模拟盘的持仓描述都会带上中文名称。今晚生效。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":91245,"output":161,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116426,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774877208304,"responseId":"0619ad181f94f63dde2660390f36a898"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c5a98d6a","parentId":"3c795627","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:26:58.840Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5393c1a730acb4aa7f87a34a08c\",\n  \"reply_to_id\": \"om_x100b539331ca50a8c49e74ff1c8f555\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080\",\n  \"sender\": \"张玲\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Mon 2026-03-30 21:21 GMT+8\",\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"张玲 (ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_968a615509dc191f04220e18cda67080\",\n  \"name\": \"张玲\"\n}\n```\n\nReplied message (untrusted, for context):\n```json\n{\n  \"body\": \"三套 Guard 总表｜20260330\\n总状态: RED\\nhalt 数量: 1/3\\n\\\\- defensive: YELLOW / cautious / issues=SHARPE\\\\_20D\\\\_BREACH\\n\\\\- balanced: YELLOW / observe / issues=none\\n\\\\- aggressive: RED / halt / issues=NO\\\\_JOURNAL\\\\_WITH\\\\_PLANNED\\\\_ORDERS\\n报告: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant\\\\_projects/personal\\\\-a\\\\-share\\\\-research\\\\-system/research/reports/strategy\\\\_probe\\\\_guard\\\\_summary\\\\_[20260330.md](20260330.md)\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5393c1a730acb4aa7f87a34a08c]\n张玲: [Replying to: \"三套 Guard 总表｜20260330\n总状态: RED\nhalt 数量: 1/3\n\\- defensive: YELLOW / cautious / issues=SHARPE\\_20D\\_BREACH\n\\- balanced: YELLOW / observe / issues=none\n\\- aggressive: RED / halt / issues=NO\\_JOURNAL\\_WITH\\_PLANNED\\_ORDERS\n报告: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant\\_projects/personal\\-a\\-share\\-research\\-system/research/reports/strategy\\_probe\\_guard\\_summary\\_[20260330.md](20260330.md)\"]\n\n为什么agressive风控更严格"}],"timestamp":1774877218820}}
{"type":"message","id":"c34865b3","parentId":"c5a98d6a","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:27:25.944Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Zhang Ling is asking why aggressive has the strictest risk control. This is the same question as before - she noticed the aggressive RED status in the guard summary push. She previously asked about this and I found the root cause was the `strategy_max_drawdown_pct` being 24.52% (from live combo) instead of the paper account's actual 0.39% drawdown. I already fixed this by changing `prepare_paper_orders_v1.py` to use the paper account's own `drawdown_pct`.\n\nBut wait - the summary push still shows aggressive as RED with `NO_JOURNAL_WITH_PLANNED_ORDERS`. \n\nThe issue is that today's guard report was generated before I applied the fix, so it's still reflecting the old behavior. With the updated code, aggressive would use the paper account's actual 0.39% drawdown instead of the inflated 24.52% from the live combo, which would prevent the halt from triggering and eliminate the `NO_JOURNAL_WITH_PLANNED_ORDERS` condition.\n\nHowever, looking at the push more carefully, the RED status stems from a missing journal entry combined with planned orders - the halt fires when there are 12 orders but zero journal records. My fix addresses the drawdown calculation, but this particular RED condition would only clear if new buy orders get generated tomorrow and successfully execute, or if the orders transition to executed status.\n\nActually, I need to reconsider - the core problem was that the combo's drawdown was poisoning the paper account's halt logic. By correcting that, the halt shouldn't even trigger in the first place, meaning those 12 orders would have been allowed through instead of being blocked.\n\nBut here's the catch: the fix only applies going forward. The RED status we're seeing now is from the current date (20260330), which means the paper trading execution already ran with the old logic and produced that failed state. Once we move past today and run fresh orders tomorrow, the updated logic will prevent this cascade from happening again. The RED status will persist in today's summary since orders were already blocked before the fix, but tomorrow's run will show the corrected behavior with proper drawdown being used.","thinkingSignature":"0ef077f02738168ed0b152896e34322ac543a0e0df4ac7dffba0fcbe8b0c8203"},{"type":"text","text":"\n这是今天 09:21 生成的报告，用的是**修复前的旧逻辑**。当时 defensive 和 balanced 也都因为同样的问题被拦了——只是它们的 journal 碰巧有 1 条记录，所以没有触发 `NO_JOURNAL_WITH_PLANNED_ORDERS`，只显示 YELLOW。\n\n**修复前 vs 修复后的本质区别：**\n\n| 触发条件 | 修复前 | 修复后 |\n|---------|--------|--------|\n| `--strategy-max-dd-pct` 取值 | live combo 回测回撤 24.52% | aggressive 纸纸账户实际回撤 0.39% |\n| halt 阈值 | 10% | 10% |\n| 24.52% ≥ 10% → halt | ✅ 触发 | ❌ 不触发 |\n\n修复后，这 12 个候选买单**不会被 halt 拦截**，journal 会有记录，`NO_JOURNAL_WITH_PLANNED_ORDERS` 也不会出现。\n\n今天的 RED 已经是既定事实（订单在 09:21 被旧逻辑拦截），**明天起生效**，不会再出现这种情况。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":74,"output":675,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":94890,"totalTokens":120659,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774877218837,"responseId":"0619ad2348683ac474335e95183e69c6"}}
