{"type":"message","id":"abf7d55d","parentId":"9533edad","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:30:37.862Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The interactive card was likely the global market morning guard or something similar. The key issue I can see is `env: node: No such file or directory` - which is the same node PATH issue we've been fixing. Let me check what's happening with the news market morning report.\n\nThe issue is the same PATH issue - the `global_market_morning_0850.log` shows:\n```\n\"info\": \"env: node: No such file or directory\"\n```\n\nThis is the cron task `NEWS_MARKET_0850` that we already fixed earlier. But wait - the fix I made was for the weibo monitor cron scripts, and the global market morning is a different skill. Let me check if the news-market skill has the same issue.","thinkingSignature":"d42f95c1d78bac14a1285a76ffd247a7c94ca13349c66b53ee6e3f6f23e3543a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_txkxg1d3a0sn_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/logs/global_market_morning_0850.log 2>/dev/null | tail -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":95561,"output":207,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":120788,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774877425016,"responseId":"0619adf17b7e0525536c2770af2b59be"}}
