{"type":"message","id":"659c1638","parentId":"64accaa3","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:40:53.012Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"My fix is in place - the `--strategy-max-dd-pct` now uses `state.get(\"drawdown_pct\", 0.0)` (paper account's own drawdown) instead of `runtime_metrics.get(\"strategy_max_dd_pct\")` (live combo dd).\n\nBut the orders file still shows the OLD block reason `strategy_max_drawdown_pct(24.5100) >= 10.0000`. This means the orders were generated BEFORE my fix was applied. Since we fixed it today, tomorrow's orders should be fine.\n\nNow let me understand the FULL picture of why paper trading underperforms:\n\n**Root causes:**\n\n\nThe halt mechanism was incorrectly using live combo's historical backtest drawdown (24.51%) instead of the paper account's actual drawdown (0.39%), which blocked all buy orders - this was the biggest performance killer. Even after that gets fixed, there's still the exit engine stopping positions at inopportune moments like on March 20th, and the breadth_strict_oos signals are stale from 27 days ago. The backtest never actually experienced these halts or stale signals, so it looks better by comparison.\n\nThe real problem is that I'm conflating backtest performance with what the paper trading actually shows - the backtest claims 55% annualized with 24.89% max drawdown, but the paper account is showing only -0.39% to -6.51%. These are measuring different things entirely, and I need to understand what's driving that gap.","thinkingSignature":"082d3533db69425613e38e5db655ac6b9f6e5c09885c6a3046552606a2ae23ef"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_jolzmuochbk7_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/paper_*_trading_metrics_20260330.json 2>/dev/null | while read f; do name=$(basename \"$f\" | sed 's/paper_//;s/_trading_metrics_20260330.json//'); echo \"=== $name ===\"; python3 -c \"import json; d=json.load(open('$f')); m=d.get('metrics',{}); print(f'年化:{m.get(\\\"annual_return_pct\\\",\\\"?\\\")}% 回撤:{m.get(\\\"max_drawdown_pct\\\",\\\"?\\\")}% 夏普:{m.get(\\\"sharpe\\\",\\\"?\\\")} 持仓天数:{m.get(\\\"position_days\\\",\\\"?\\\")}')\"; done"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":90510,"output":509,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116039,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774878033281,"responseId":"0619b0514cbccd3be7d833d89ba1fed0"}}
