{"type":"message","id":"5e86dccf","parentId":"15435c14","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:41:06.530Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Wait, the backtest result has annual_return_pct=55.07%, but the paper trading metrics show negative Sharpe. Let me also check the breadth_strict_oos metrics.","thinkingSignature":"1b0ac701ddf9121b59583f7bb36bc5724087aa56949129891b768cb33124d16a"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_g0i8z34ybp9u_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 -c \"\nimport json\n# 检查 breadth_strict_oos 为什么仓位只有 31%\nd = json.load(open('/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/breadth_strict_oos_paper_latest.json'))\nprint('信号日期:', d['signal_date'])\nprint('已过期天数:', d['absolute_lag_days'])\nprint('当前状态:', d['execution_status'])\nprint('目标仓位:', d['target_position_pct'], '%')\nprint('实际仓位:', round(d['market_value']/d['total_value']*100,1), '%')\nprint('漂移:', d['target_drift_pct'], '%')\nprint('买入列表:', len(d['buy_list']), '卖出列表:', len(d['sell_list']))\nprint('持仓数:', d['position_count'])\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":90688,"output":240,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115948,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774878053194,"responseId":"0619b065ef63510d5af545a6c3e171b6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"be1105a7","parentId":"5e86dccf","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:41:06.657Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_g0i8z34ybp9u_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Traceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"<string>\", line 10, in <module>\nKeyError: 'target_drift_pct'\n信号日期: 2026-03-03\n已过期天数: 27\n当前状态: signal_stale_hold\n目标仓位: 80.0 %\n实际仓位: 31.2 %\n\n(Command exited with code 1)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":1,"durationMs":49,"aggregated":"Traceback (most recent call last):\n  File \"<string>\", line 10, in <module>\nKeyError: 'target_drift_pct'\n信号日期: 2026-03-03\n已过期天数: 27\n当前状态: signal_stale_hold\n目标仓位: 80.0 %\n实际仓位: 31.2 %\n\n(Command exited with code 1)","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774878066643}}
{"type":"message","id":"e013a021","parentId":"be1105a7","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:41:38.937Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, now I have a clear picture. Let me compile all the issues and explain them to Zhang Ling.","thinkingSignature":"abac38b54c1050daf9dc730cb4ad4d344f091eb9ebae9e2f5c4697deabec2ba4"},{"type":"text","text":"---\n\n**全面排查结论：模拟盘表现远差于回测，问题不在\"运气不好\"，在系统本身。**\n\n---\n\n## 一、核心对比\n\n| 维度 | 回测结果 | 模拟盘现状 |\n|------|---------|-----------|\n| 年化收益 | **+55.07%**（2015-2026） | **-0.4% 至 -6.5%**（实跑约20天） |\n| 最大回撤 | 24.89% | 0.39%~6.51% |\n| 夏普比率 | 2.794 | -4.2 至 -4.6（负值，极差） |\n| 原因 | 理论最优 | halt/止盈止损/信号过期 |\n\n---\n\n## 二、问题链路（按严重程度）\n\n### 🔴 1. 策略级熔断 halt — 最大祸首\n**所有 12 个候选买单被 `strategy_max_dd_pct(24.51%) >= 10%` 拦截**\n- defensive、balanced、aggressive 三盘全部零买入\n- 根因：风控层引用了 live combo 的历史回测回撤 24.51%，而非纸纸账户实际回撤 0.39%\n- 状态：✅ 已修复，明天生效\n\n### 🔴 2. Exit Engine 止盈止损时机差\n- **3月20日**：aggressive 三只持仓全部触发追踪止盈卖出，但**恰好卖在局部最低点**\n- 之后市场反弹，三盘空仓踏空\n- **持仓平均亏损 -7.42%**，止损比例偏高（单票亏7.42%才触发止损，说明入场时机本身差）\n\n### 🟡 3. Exit_dual / Exit_tight 严重亏损 -6.5%\n- 3月12日建仓，3月25-26日触发止损，**持仓13天最大浮亏 -7.46%~-7.07%**\n- 之后回升但已止损卖出，**亏损坐实**\n- 问题本质：这两个策略是\"验证exit阈值\"的实验盘，本身就是拿来测试极端止损的，不是主策略\n\n### 🟡 4. 预测信号过期 27 天（breadth_strict_oos）\n- 信号最新日期停在 2026-03-03（27天前），此后无新信号\n- 目标仓位 80%，实际只运行到 31%，漂移 -48.8%\n- 策略完全暂停，等于空转\n- 需重新跑 Qlib 每日特征/预测流程刷新 `ml_predictions.csv`\n\n### 🟡 5. Alpha55 完全未启动\n- 净值 1000000.00（初始资金），零操作，零收益\n- date_tag 停留在 20260327，说明今日没有新信号或执行\n\n---\n\n## 三、真实原因总结\n\n回测（+55%）是**理想市场下的理论最优路径**，但实盘中：\n\n1. **halt 熔断太激进** → 错过大部分交易日\n2. **止盈止损太灵敏** → 卖在反转前，亏损后被动止损\n3. **预测信号断供** → 策略空转无法交易\n4. **Exit_dual/Tight 是测试盘** → 本身不代表主策略预期\n\n---\n\n## 四、修复优先级\n\n| 优先级 | 动作 | 解决哪个问题 |\n|--------|------|-------------|\n| ✅ 明天自动 | halt 修复生效后三盘恢复买 | 问题1 |\n| 需决定 | exit_engine 参数调参（止盈回撤4%→6%） | 问题2 |\n| 需跑数据 | Qlib 每日预测刷新 ml_predictions.csv | 问题3 + 4 |\n| 需确认 | alpha55 为什么零信号 | 问题5 |\n\n要不要我把 exit_engine 的止盈止损参数调一调？或者先跑 Qlib 预测刷新解决 breadth_strict_oos 的信号问题？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":89784,"output":856,"cacheRead":25020,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115660,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774878066658,"responseId":"0619b073520913cc33338bc438d9c2cc"}}
