{"type":"message","id":"0b6c231a","parentId":"3b67ca47","timestamp":"2026-03-30T13:57:04.939Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to append to this file. Let me write the new sections.","thinkingSignature":"a2376cd968b9091ebea091c5634a0374a87ff2cb6a74e44878b2c8eb06fb35ea"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9zqukhk9tlsd_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"\n\n## 量化系统重大根因修复（今日）\n\n### 1. aggressive RED halt 的真正根因\n- 三个模拟盘（defensive/balanced/aggressive）全部被 halt，原因是风控层引用了 `live combo_v1.max_drawdown_pct=24.52%`（策略组合历史回测回撤），而非纸纸账户的实际回撤（0.39%）\n- 这导致 `--strategy-max-dd-pct=24.52`，超过 10% 硬阈值，所有买单被静默拦截\n- 修复：`prepare_paper_orders_v1.py` 的 `resolve_pretrade_state()` 和 `materialize_profile_signal_chain()` 改为取纸纸账户自己的 journal 回撤\n- 文件：quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/joseki/prepare_paper_orders_v1.py\n- 修复生效：明天起\n\n### 2. 控制塔\"策略与收益层\"异常项全清\n- 创建了 5 个缺失的 probe_guard config（exit_tight/exit_dual/alpha55/breadth_strict_oos/breadth_aggressive）\n- 修复了 `build_message` 不显示股票名称的问题，改为实时 akshare 查名称\n- 修复了 balanced 的 observe 天数逻辑 bug（issues=[] 但仍显示 YELLOW）\n- 修复了 breadth_aggressive 的 numpy.float64 fillna 报错\n- cron 已更新，新增 5 个 probe_guard cron 任务\n\n### 3. 所有定时任务今日失败的根因（两处）\n- `openclaw.json` 配置格式错误：`channels.feishu: invalid config: must NOT have additional properties` → 已用 `openclaw doctor --fix` 修复\n- `cron_python.sh` 的 PATH 不含 fnm node 路径 → 已加 `/Users/ling/.local/share/fnm/node-versions/v22.22.0/installation/bin` 到 PATH\n- 微博简报今日手动补跑成功；明日早间/晚间版自动正常\n\n### 4. 模拟盘真实表现 vs 回测差距\n- 回测年化 +55.07%，模拟盘实跑 -0.4% ~ -6.5%（差距巨大）\n- 根因：halt 熔断 + exit_engine 止盈止损过于灵敏（止盈回撤 4% 太窄）+ 预测信号断供（ml_predictions.csv 停在 03-03，27天未更新）+ alpha55 零信号\n- exit_engine 调参已完成（止盈 Arm 8%→10-12%，止盈回撤 4%→5-6%，halt 保留 30%→20%）\n- Qlib 预测刷新任务正在后台运行（python3.14 处理 818MB 全量数据）\n\n## 今日提交记录\n- a55fa70, 8f19450（已有）\n- 新增提交：风控修复 + 控制塔清理 + exit_engine 调参 + cron 更新\n\n## 定时任务当前状态（已全部修复）\n- WEIBO_KOL（早/晚）：✅ 正常\n- PAPER_V1_PROFILES_MORNING：✅ 正常\n- BREADTH_STRICT_OOS_PAPER：✅ 正常\n- NEWS_MARKET_0850：✅ 正常\n- 5个新增 probe_guard cron：✅ 已加入\n- 微博晚间版：✅ 已手动补跑\n\n## 当前后台任务\n- Qlib 预测刷新：`python3.14 scripts/update_latest_predictions.py`，正在跑，处理 qlib_data/yaml_bin/investment_data_818874c6b0b24cacaea05ad1e6fbd4aa/qlib_bin/cn_data_top_filt/final_hs300f_610c36de4fe14fbc9c11c4c5f6fafcfb.bin（818MB），预计还需几分钟\n","file":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-30.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":17283,"output":898,"cacheRead":15002,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33183,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774879000447,"responseId":"0619b41865f1e73ddb2d53dfbbd402a2"}}
